NK036(chi)030:1: // kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer gyi rnam thar mthong ba don ldan bzhugs so //
NK036(chi)030:2: swa sti sarba mam ga la sid+d+hi pha la hoh
NK036(chi)030:3: bla ma'i rnam thar mthong ba don ldan zhes bya
NK036(chi)030:4: ba / brgyud pa gsum gyi bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK036(chi)030:5: gang gi thog mar 'gro don thugs bskyed nas //
NK036(chi)030:6: bar du grangs med dbu la khur chen khyer //
NK036(chi)030:7: tha mar byang chub mngon par sangs rgyas nas //
NK036(chi)030:8: lha mdzes sras mchog lum+bi'i tshal bltams bzhin //
NK036(chi)030:9: skyes mchog 'di yang de yi rjes 'gro ba'i //
NK036(chi)030:10: sngon rol bskal pa mang por tshogs bsags nas //
NK036(chi)030:11: bar du brtson pa'i go cha mtha' yas shing //
NK036(chi)030:12: tha mar don gnyis mdzad de gtsug gis mchod //
NK036(chi)030:13: bdag nyid chen po dri med 'od zer gyi //
NK036(chi)030:14: rnam thar nam mkha'i mtha' dang rgya mtsho'i khyon //
NK036(chi)030:15: tshu rol blo yis rtogs par dka' na yang //
NK036(chi)030:16: bka' drin dran dang phyi rabs don du spro //
NK036(chi)030:17: chur nyal tshal na rta bdun shar ba yis //
NK036(chi)030:18: rkang drug dga' ston 'phel bar gyur pa ltar //
NK036(chi)030:19: bdag blo'i snying gi pad+mo kha phyes la //
NK036(chi)030:20: 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i spobs pa bskyed du gsol /
NK036(chi)030:22: 67&&& / de yang 'dir skyes mchog de'i bka' drin mi 'dor ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:23: phyi rabs skal ldan rnams kyi don du /
NK036(chi)030:24: chos rje rin po che'i rnam thar mthong ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:26: rtogs pa'i tshul mdo tsam zhig yi ger 'god pa la /
NK036(chi)030:27: bla ma dam pa rnams kyis byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK036(chi)030:28: mkha' 'gro chos skyong gi tshogs rnams kyis stong grogs mdzod cig /
NK036(chi)030:29: de la bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad gangs
NK036(chi)030:30: chen mtsho'i skus zhing khams thams cad khyab cing sku
NK036(chi)030:31: la zhing khams thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK036(chi)030:32: zhabs rdo rje skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa'i phyag gnyis mnyam gzhag gi mthil na /
NK036(chi)030:33: lhung bzed spos chus gtams par me tog nyi shu rtsa lnga brtsegs mar gnas pa'i bcu gsum pa /
NK036(chi)030:34: thugs ka dpal gyi be'u'i thad pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru gcig
NK036(chi)030:35: gi steng na gzhi dang snying po me tog gis
NK036(chi)030:37: thub pa'i dbang po 'di'i gdul zhing 'dzam gling bye ba phrag brgyar gnas pa la /
NK036(chi)030:38: gling bzhi las lho phyogs 'dzam gling /
NK036(chi)030:39: sa'i lte ba rdo rje gdan las dpag tshad brgya
NK036(chi)030:40: lhag gis bgrod pa'i sa phyogs g.yo ru gra phu
NK036(chi)030:42: slob dpon chen po pad+ma'i dngos slob dpal rta mgrin gyi grub thob gdung rus ngan lam /
NK036(chi)030:43: mtshan btsun pa rgyal ba mchog dbyangs zhes bya ba
NK036(chi)030:44: de'i gdung rus kyi brgyud pa zam ma chad pa
NK036(chi)030:45: de'i mi rabs nyi shu rtsa lnga song ba na
NK036(chi)030:46: / a mes lha srung zhes bya ba bdud rtsi sman gyi grub pa thob pa /
NK036(chi)030:47: dgung lo brgya dang lnga thub pa slob dpon bstan bsrung zhes bya ba gcig dang /
NK036(chi)030:48: yum mkha' 'gro'i sprul pa 'brog bzang bsod nams rgyan gnyis kyi sras su 'khrungs pa'i ltas la /
NK036(chi)030:49: yum gyi rmi lam du seng+ge chen po gcig gi
NK036(chi)030:50: dpral bar nyi ma gnyis dus gcig la shar ba
NK036(chi)030:51: 'od zer khyil khyil mo rang gi lus la thim
NK036(chi)030:52: pa rmis te / dus tshod sa pho spre'u'i lo zla ba gnyis pa'i tshes brgyad /
NK036(chi)030:53: skar ma rgyal 'dzoms la sku bltams pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)030:54: bud med nag mo ral gri thogs pa bzhin dang mche ba gnyer ba zhig na re /
NK036(chi)030:55: ngas bsrungs pa yin zer nas phyag tu blang /
NK036(chi)030:56: slar yum la gtad de mi snang bar gyur to //
NK036(chi)030:57: de ni nam gru re ma ti'o //
NK036(chi)030:58: yang lan gcig yur ma byed dus /
NK036(chi)030:59: mu khar bsnyal nas yod pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)030:60: yum bya ba gcig gis brel nas yod dus /
NK036(chi)030:61: ser ba babs pas bu chung brjed nas nang du phyin pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:62: dran nas zhing khar bltas pas bu chung mi 'dug nas /
NK036(chi)030:63: ngu zhing nang du yong ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:64: sngar gyi bud med nag mo des /
NK036(chi)030:65: bu chung mdzod nas khyer byung ste /
NK036(chi)030:66: ral gri brdeg la khad byas nas sprul pa'i sku
NK036(chi)030:67: la brnyas pa byed pa zer nas mi snang bar
NK036(chi)030:68: gyur to // rang bzhin dus thams cad du /
NK036(chi)030:69: nam gru re ma t+ai gzugs tha dad pa'i sgo nas 'bral ba med par zhabs tog byas so //
NK036(chi)030:70: de yang sprul sku yin par pad+ma'i bka' chems las lung bstan zin pa yin te /
NK036(chi)030:71: dus kyi tha ma la rgyal ba mchog dbyangs kyi
NK036(chi)030:72: rigs rgyud kyi tha ma 'jam dbyangs kyis sprul pa
NK036(chi)030:73: gcig gis sngags kyi bstan pa dar bar byed cing
NK036(chi)030:74: / de nas yang brgyud pa gnyis kyi bar dar bar byed pa yin te /
NK036(chi)030:76: &&& / lum+bi'i tshal na don grub bltams pa'i tshe //
NK036(chi)030:77: lha dbang klu yi rgyal pos khrul gsol nas //
NK036(chi)030:78: dar dkar sle'usa blangs nas shis pa brjod //
NK036(chi)030:79: dga' ba'i mdangs phyungs legs par mchod pa ltar //
NK036(chi)030:80: skyes mchog 'di yang bltams par gyur pa'i tshe //
NK036(chi)030:81: nam gru re ma t+ai yi phyag gnyis kyis //
NK036(chi)030:82: legs par blangs nas bsrung zhing skyob bo zhes //
NK036(chi)030:83: slar yang yum la gtad nas mi snang gyur //
NK036(chi)030:84: zhes pa ni bltams pa'i tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK036(chi)030:85: de ltar chung ngu nas dad pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:88: chu pho byi ba dgung lo lnga nas 'bri klog zhib par mkhyen /
NK036(chi)030:89: shing stag bdun la yab las bde gshegs 'dus pa /
NK036(chi)030:93: sman rtsis la sogs pa mkhyen par mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:94: me 'brug dgung lo dgu la grwa phyi tshong 'dus su /
NK036(chi)030:96: brgyad stong pa gnyis brgya tshar bton pas thugs la chud /
NK036(chi)030:97: sa mo lug dgung lo bcu gnyis la bsam yas su mkhan po bsam rin pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:98: slob dpon lha kun dga' 'od zer las rab tu
NK036(chi)030:99: byung nas tshul khrims blo gros zhes mtshan gsol te
NK036(chi)030:101: bcu gnyis la grwa skor dang bshad pa mdzad do //
NK036(chi)030:102: zas gtsang sras po khab nas mngon phyung ste //
NK036(chi)030:103: rnam dag drung du rab byung bsnyen par rdzogs //
NK036(chi)030:104: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs gzigs pa'i tshul bstan nas //
NK036(chi)030:105: 'gro ba'i kha lo gyen la bsgyur bar mdzad //
NK036(chi)030:106: de ltar dam pa 'di yang bsam yas su //
NK036(chi)030:107: bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba yin dgongs nas //
NK036(chi)030:108: nyan cing bshad nas phul du phyin par mdzad //
NK036(chi)030:109: thub chen rjes 'gro de la gus pas 'dud //
NK036(chi)030:110: de nas dgung lo bcu drug la /
NK036(chi)030:111: slob dpon bkra shis rin chen la /
NK036(chi)030:115: bde mchog dril bu pa'i dbang dang bcas la /
NK036(chi)030:116: phyag rdor 'khor lo chen po'i dbang gdams par bcas pa zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:117: slob dpon dbang yes las dus 'khor /
NK036(chi)030:118: gsar ma'i rgyud 'bum la sogs rgyud sde mang po dang /
NK036(chi)030:119: za lung rin po che las zhang tshal pa'i chos skor /
NK036(chi)030:121: dam pa'i zhi byed snga phyi bar gsum /
NK036(chi)030:122: ma gcig gi gcod rnam drug la sogs pa gsan cing /
NK036(chi)030:123: dgung long bcu dgu sa pho stag la gsang phur byon nas /
NK036(chi)030:124: mkhas pa'i phul du phyin pa bla brang pa chos dpal ldan rgyal mtshan pa /
NK036(chi)030:125: chos grags gnyis kyi drung du /
NK036(chi)030:128: tshad btus rnams kyi nyan bshad lo drug zhun thar legs par bcad de /
NK036(chi)030:129: mgon po byams pa'i rgyud bla mar /
NK036(chi)030:130: rnam rtog las gzhan de dag gi //
NK036(chi)030:131: spang rgyu gzhan med de yi phyir //
NK036(chi)030:132: thos pa de phyir thos pa mchog /
NK036(chi)030:133: ces dang mthun par dam pa de nyid kyis //
NK036(chi)030:134: thos bsam gnas la blo gros legs sbyangs nas //
NK036(chi)030:135: mi shes mun sel rmongs pa'i tshang tshing bsregs //
NK036(chi)030:136: shes bya rab gzigs mkhas pa'i pha mthar phyin //
NK036(chi)030:137: ces pa 'di yang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK036(chi)030:139: mi g.yo ba dang dbyangs can ma shes rab gsal byed la sogs pa'i sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK036(chi)030:140: lha so so'i zhal gzigs shing gsung thos pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:141: khyad par dbyangs can ma dang mjal dus /
NK036(chi)030:142: dbyangs can gyi phyag mthil du bzhag nas gling bzhi
NK036(chi)030:143: ri rab dang bcas pa zhag bdun du gzigs so
NK036(chi)030:144: // de nas mgrin pa longs spyod kyi rtsa kha bye ste blo gros phyogs med du rgyas te /
NK036(chi)030:145: gsang phu la sogs pa'i rig grwar bsam yas pa lung mang pa zhes grags so //
NK036(chi)030:146: gzhan yang skad gnyis smra ba blo gros brtan pa'i
NK036(chi)030:147: drung du tshad ma sde bdun gyi rnam bshad dang
NK036(chi)030:148: / shes rab snying po'i rgya cher 'grel gyi bshad pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:149: ting nge 'dzin rgyal po la sogs pa'i zab mo mdo lnga'i bshad pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:150: snyan ngag me long gzhung 'grel la sogs pa mang du gsan no //
NK036(chi)030:151: de ltar lung dang man ngag dang /
NK036(chi)030:152: rig pa dang snyan ngag dang /
NK036(chi)030:153: sdebs sbyor la dbang 'byor pas phyogs tha dad du byon nas /
NK036(chi)030:154: mkhas grub kyi bla ma du ma las mdo dang rgyud dang man ngag rnams mang du zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:155: slob dpon gzhon nu don grub las rnying ma'i rgyud 'bum /
NK036(chi)030:156: 'dus mdo sgyu 'phrul sems phyogs la sogs pa mang du gsan no //
NK036(chi)030:157: slob dpon gzhon nu rgyal po las bka' dang po bden pa bzhi'i 'grel pa gtam gyi tshogs dang /
NK036(chi)030:158: bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i 'grel pa rig pa'i tshogs drug rtsa ba shes rab /
NK036(chi)030:163: tha ma don dam nges pa'i tshogs 'grel pa chos
NK036(chi)030:164: dbyings bstod pa la sogs pa'i bstod tshogs zhus shing
NK036(chi)030:165: / slob dpon gzhon nu rdo rje las spyod 'jug /
NK036(chi)030:168: snyan brgyud mang du zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:169: mkhan po las khro phu ba'i chos skor /
NK036(chi)030:180: tshul lnga bcu pa la sogs pa'i lung mang po gsan cing /
NK036(chi)030:181: chos rje karma pa rang byung rdo rje las sbyor drug gegs sel dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)030:184: thugs rje chen po rgyal ba rgya mtsho /
NK036(chi)030:185: thugs rje chen po rgyal po lugs /
NK036(chi)030:189: gshed dmar nag rnams gsan zhing /
NK036(chi)030:190: slob dpon dbang yes las sbyor drug bsnyen sgrub yi dam dmar khrid /
NK036(chi)030:193: 'jigs byed rwa lugs kyi rgyud rtog pa bdun pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:194: gsum pa dbang gdams ngag rdzogs rim dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)030:195: rlung 'khor dzam b+ha la skor gsum /
NK036(chi)030:198: slob dpon ston tshul las drang srong gzhung skyes kyi
NK036(chi)030:199: dngul chu'i bcud len dang bye ma'i bcud len zhus
NK036(chi)030:200: shing / bla ma 'jam dbyangs pa las /
NK036(chi)030:202: me mkha' rgya mtsho'i lnga bsdus /
NK036(chi)030:209: de kho na nyid bsdus pa ta tha sam ha /
NK036(chi)030:213: rab gnas don gsal la sogs pa zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:214: sa skya ba'i bla ma bdag nyid chen po'i drung du /
NK036(chi)030:216: rgyud gsum gyi gdams pa kha tshang zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:217: bla ma khro phu ba las /
NK036(chi)030:218: rdo rje phreng ba gur mgon dregs mgon la sogs pa zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:220: chos dbang lugs kyi gsang ba yongs rdzogs /
NK036(chi)030:221: thugs rje chen po yang snying 'dus pa /
NK036(chi)030:222: rdzogs chen sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK036(chi)030:227: rgya mtsho du ru ka'i gtad rgya /
NK036(chi)030:231: khrom sgrub pa la sogs zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:233: tshe bdag p+aa la pa tra /
NK036(chi)030:236: ma mo dug gi spu gri /
NK036(chi)030:241: ser ba srung 'bebs la sogs pa zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:250: seng zhon sgrub thabs la sogs pa zhus shing /
NK036(chi)030:251: de yang sngar gsang phur bzhugs dus /
NK036(chi)030:252: khams pa rnams kyis gnas khang gcig nas gcig tu lan bdun phud pas /
NK036(chi)030:253: khro phu ba dkon mchog dpal dang lhan cig bzhugs shing yod pa la /
NK036(chi)030:255: bla brang pa chos dpal bzang pos khro phu ba la shog gsungs nas /
NK036(chi)030:256: dge bshes bsam yas pa 'di 'dir chags na grwa
NK036(chi)030:257: sa 'di la phan pa zhig 'ong ba 'dug ste
NK036(chi)030:258: / khams pa ngan pa 'di rnams kyis sdod du mi 'jug pa 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)030:259: ja 'di khyer la khong gal che ba rnams la drong /
NK036(chi)030:262: nga'i yang lab pa yin gyis gsungs nas /
NK036(chi)030:263: ja zho phyed dang snam bu gnyis bskur ba khyer nas /
NK036(chi)030:267: do dgongs mi khom par yod zer nas gshegs so //
NK036(chi)030:268: phyir nang tho rangs khres po bsgrogs nas de 'gro ba yin /
NK036(chi)030:269: nga'i shul na khong rnams zo zhig gsungs nas bzhud do //
NK036(chi)030:270: grogs po gcig yar byung ba dang lo ts+aa ba chen po'i sku 'bum rtsar 'phrad byung bas /
NK036(chi)030:271: khyod 'gro ba i yin zer bas /
NK036(chi)030:272: nga khams pa'i thad du sdod sa mi 'dug pas 'gro zer /
NK036(chi)030:273: khyod rtsom pa la ni thogs pa med /
NK036(chi)030:274: khong rnams la ngan smras kyi tshigs bcad cig 'jog rgyu yin nam zer bas /
NK036(chi)030:275: shog bu bre kha gang la shongs thang zhig bris nas chos khrir brlan yod /
NK036(chi)030:276: da dung 'di nas dum gcig bskur bas /
NK036(chi)030:277: 'di khyer cig gsungs nas rkyen la khams 'dus pa ka kha sum cu mdzad nas yar bskur /
NK036(chi)030:278: khong rnams kyis chos kyi khri'i yig ngan de dar du ma ster /
NK036(chi)030:279: ka kha sum cu 'di rgya yul yan chad du dar bar gyur to //
NK036(chi)030:280: de nas skabs gcig tu dbur stod la yar bsod snyoms la byon pa la /
NK036(chi)030:281: na bza' la yang chos sham stod thung bod phrug
NK036(chi)030:282: dur kha'i phyam tse tho re ba zhig dang mtha'
NK036(chi)030:283: gnyis su ma lhung ba tsam las med /
NK036(chi)030:284: cha mad'i yul khang zhig tu bzhugs pa'i nub mo
NK036(chi)030:285: dbus stod nas yod pa'i dge bshes gcig kyang der
NK036(chi)030:286: bsdad du 'dug pa de na re /
NK036(chi)030:288: nga gsang phu nas yong ba yin byas pas /
NK036(chi)030:289: slob gnyer ci byas zer bas /
NK036(chi)030:292: tshad ma la sogs pa shes /
NK036(chi)030:293: khyed gang nas yin gsungs pas /
NK036(chi)030:296: btsun pa ni bya yul du byas /
NK036(chi)030:297: slob gnyer ni dbu ma 'jug pa legs po zhig shes zer bas /
NK036(chi)030:298: 'o na rgya ma na grub thob lcog la'i sgrub
NK036(chi)030:299: khang brag khung zhig yod zer ba de ci 'dra
NK036(chi)030:301: brag khung legs po zhig yod ci byed zer /
NK036(chi)030:302: bsod snyoms la nas rkyal pa bzang ba gang rnyed na /
NK036(chi)030:303: der dgun bzhugs gcig byas na bsams gsungs pas /
NK036(chi)030:305: nga la skor 'di na char nas bsdu rgyu zhig yod /
NK036(chi)030:307: grong der sngags pa bu phrug ma sos pa zhig 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)030:308: khyed kyis rta mgrin nag po'i sbyin sreg e shes zer /
NK036(chi)030:310: 'o na nga cag byon zer nas sbyin sreg mdzad pas /
NK036(chi)030:311: nas rkyal pa bzang ba gang phul /
NK036(chi)030:312: de nas dge bshes de dang bsdongs nas lcog la'i brag khung du byon /
NK036(chi)030:313: zla ba brgyad du mtshams byed pa'i dam bca' mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:314: mun khang zhig mdzad nas bzhes pa der drangs /
NK036(chi)030:315: tho rangs kyi thun la dge bshes de la phar phyin thun che ba re gsung /
NK036(chi)030:316: zla ba lnga song ba'i tho rangs khar /
NK036(chi)030:317: nam mkhar sil snyan gyi sgra dang /
NK036(chi)030:318: glu dbyangs snyan po gsan nas gzigs pas /
NK036(chi)030:319: lung pa'i mda' na bye ma'i ri chung dang /
NK036(chi)030:320: 'bab chu gcig yod pa'i sa nas yar /
NK036(chi)030:321: rta gser khrab dang dril bu g.yer khas brgyan pa zhig la /
NK036(chi)030:322: bud med lo bcu drug pa'i na tshod tsam za 'og gi gos dang /
NK036(chi)030:324: gser gyi pa tras gdong g.yogs pa gcig zhon nas
NK036(chi)030:325: byon pa'i thu ba la 'jus nas 'phags ma thugs
NK036(chi)030:327: rin po che'i dbu rgyan gcig 'dug pa de phud nas khong gi mgo la bskon nas /
NK036(chi)030:328: dus 'di nas bzung ste byin gyis brlab cing dngos grub sbyin par bya'o //
NK036(chi)030:330: de'i byin brlabs kyis zla ba gcig gi bar du /
NK036(chi)030:331: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin phyam brdal
NK036(chi)030:332: rig 'dzin chen po ku ma r+aa dza dang mjal
NK036(chi)030:334: de nas mtshams bkrol nas yab yum gyi don du kun rig gi cho ga brgya rtsa brgyad mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:335: slob dpon la bstan tshul gyi cho ga yang 'di
NK036(chi)030:336: tsam mdzad pas byin brlabs yod nges snyam nas dbang
NK036(chi)030:339: slob dpon chu len du song ring /
NK036(chi)030:341: rtsig pa bya lcag ma byed pa'i lcags kyi ldel
NK036(chi)030:342: ka dang bcas pas dkyil 'khor legs pa gcig bzhengs
NK036(chi)030:343: tshar 'dug na sngags pa phyug po bza' tshang 'khor
NK036(chi)030:344: gcig dang / pho mo sum cu tsam gyis dbang zhus so //
NK036(chi)030:345: kye ma kyi hud mgon po thugs rje can //
NK036(chi)030:346: mi mngon dbyings nas bdag la gzigs mdzod la //
NK036(chi)030:347: ngag gi dbang po'i mkhyen rab 'od stong gis //
NK036(chi)030:348: bdag blo'i snying gi mun pa myur du sol //
NK036(chi)030:349: de nas dgung lo nyer bdun la /
NK036(chi)030:350: rig 'dzin chen po'i drung du 'byon pa la bsam yas na mar byon par /
NK036(chi)030:351: g.yag sde pan chen dang 'phrad pas /
NK036(chi)030:352: da khyod gar 'gro thams cad chos rje karma pa
NK036(chi)030:353: las chos zhu ba la yar 'tshogs pas der 'gro
NK036(chi)030:355: nga yar stod rkyam gyi phu na rig 'dzin chen
NK036(chi)030:356: po ku ma r+aa dza bzhugs zer ba la mjal
NK036(chi)030:358: rkyam phur byon pas rig 'dzin chen po dpon slob
NK036(chi)030:359: rnams sbra cha ther bdun cu tsam mdzad nas bzhugs
NK036(chi)030:360: pa dang mjal / bla ma'i zhal nas mdang lha'i
NK036(chi)030:361: bya yin zer ba'i bya ya mtshan can gcig la
NK036(chi)030:362: bya bran stong gis bskor nas nga'i dpe cha khyer
NK036(chi)030:363: nas phyogs tha dad du song ba rmis /
NK036(chi)030:364: de khyed la lta ba yin par 'dug /
NK036(chi)030:365: nga'i chos 'di'i brgyud pa 'dzin pa zhig yong bar 'dug gsungs nas dgyes tshor chen po mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:366: 'di dus dgung lo nyer bdun 'gro gsungs /
NK036(chi)030:367: dpyid ka der lung stong gcig nas gcig tu lan
NK036(chi)030:368: dgu 'pho skyas byas nas gzhi re zin dus skyas
NK036(chi)030:369: re byas pas lus ngag la gzan par byung /
NK036(chi)030:370: gos ngan pas nye gnas btsun chung 'ga' yod pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:371: bskor khyi yang sdang bar byung /
NK036(chi)030:372: khrid sang nyin 'dzugs pa'i do dgongs khrid gnyer pa gnyis kyis tshogs bre chen po zhig khyer nas /
NK036(chi)030:373: dge bshes bsam yas pa'i chos khral gar yod dbang
NK036(chi)030:374: gang rgyud dang bcas pa zhu ba la nas khal
NK036(chi)030:375: bdun re dgos pa yin zer bas /
NK036(chi)030:376: nga la ni bre gang yang med chos thob par
NK036(chi)030:377: byed pa yin gsungs pas bsdad pa yin byas pas
NK036(chi)030:378: / khrid pa 'di tsam gcig gi chos khral sus 'jal zer ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:379: skye ba snga ma tshogs ma bsags pas dka' las de tsam zhig byas pas /
NK036(chi)030:380: chos khral la sdug nas 'gro dgos pa 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)030:381: mi la ngo tsha nam langs tsa na lung pa
NK036(chi)030:382: 'di'i mdor slebs pa byed dgos dgongs nas tho rangs
NK036(chi)030:384: dge bshes bsam yas pa khyed la da lta chos rje'i drung du shog gsungs zer bas /
NK036(chi)030:385: nged rang 'gro rtsis yin yang gsung bcag na mi nyan dgongs nas zhabs drung du phyinapasa /
NK036(chi)030:387: spra spro ma byed par bzhugs la ja 'thung gsung /
NK036(chi)030:388: khrid gnyer pa gnyis la shog gyis gsungs nas /
NK036(chi)030:389: tsha ba gnang ba'i gral du dge bshes 'di'i chos khral nang nas 'debs pa yin khong ma gtser /
NK036(chi)030:390: nga la da res kyi chos nyan 'di tsho thams cad las khong dga' ba yin gsung /
NK036(chi)030:391: e ma ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i tshul //
NK036(chi)030:392: chos 'phags drung du rtag ngu mjal ba dang //
NK036(chi)030:393: byams mgon drung na thogs med mjal ba ltar //
NK036(chi)030:394: dam pas dam pa brten pa 'di ni mtshar /
NK036(chi)030:395: phye bre gsum dang dngul chu ril bu nyi shu
NK036(chi)030:396: rtsa gcig gis zla ba gnyis kyi gsol ba mdzad
NK036(chi)030:397: cing / kha ba babs dus sgye nang du bzhugs nas /
NK036(chi)030:398: gos gdan gnyis ka'i go bcad cing /
NK036(chi)030:399: chos phyogs su dka' ba mang du spyad nas /
NK036(chi)030:400: bla ma'i drung du chos bka' yang mang bar gsan nas /
NK036(chi)030:401: gter ma nyang lugs kyi gu ru zhi drag byin rlabs lu gu rgyud /
NK036(chi)030:402: bka' brgyad phag nag dmar mo la sogs kyi sgrub thabs mang po dang /
NK036(chi)030:405: kun bzang che ba rang gnas /
NK036(chi)030:407: klong chen rab 'byams kyi shes bya mtha' gcod /
NK036(chi)030:408: phyi skor nang skor gsang skor gyi rgyud mang po dang /
NK036(chi)030:409: khyad par gsang ba bla na med pa'i dbang bzhi /
NK036(chi)030:410: zab mo pod bzhi phran dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)030:411: rgyud bcu bdun t+ai ka dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)030:412: man ngag brgya dang bcu dgu phran tshegs dang bcas pa /
NK036(chi)030:413: bka' srung e ka tsa ti'i sgrub thabs legs ldan lcam dral /
NK036(chi)030:415: dam can gyi sgrub thabs skor dang bcas pa la sogs zhus zhing /
NK036(chi)030:416: bstan pa dam pa'i cha lugs ma lus pa /
NK036(chi)030:417: bka' yi bstan pa'i babs rjes gnang dang bcas nas /
NK036(chi)030:418: gnang bar mdzad de bstan pas /
NK036(chi)030:419: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur bas /
NK036(chi)030:420: chos kyi rgyal por gyur cing gang gis mthong ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:423: reg pa thams cad gdod ma'i sa la 'god pa'i mthu chen po mnga' ba yin no //
NK036(chi)030:424: gdod ma'i mgon dang rnam dbyer mi phyed cing //
NK036(chi)030:425: 'gro ba'i don du thugs rjes thabs chen 'gyed //
NK036(chi)030:426: theg mchog snying po'i char rgyun rgya che bas //
NK036(chi)030:427: skal bzang lta spyod lo tog rgyas mdzad bstod //
NK036(chi)030:428: de nas mchims phur lo bdun gyi bar dam bca' sgrub pa mdzad dus /
NK036(chi)030:429: lhun grub sgang du phag mo nag mo'i zhal zhag bdun mthong /
NK036(chi)030:430: de nas o rgyan drag sgrub /
NK036(chi)030:431: che mchog dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag bzhi bcu
NK036(chi)030:432: zhe gnyis pa la bka' brgyad kyi lha tshogs bdun
NK036(chi)030:433: brgya nyi shu rtsa lngas bskor ba skabs skabs su
NK036(chi)030:434: gzigs so // gnod sbyin dzam lhas nor bu gcig phul ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:435: rdo rje g.yu sgron mas zhal bstan nas /
NK036(chi)030:436: rang gi phyi sgrub nang sgrub bla na med pa dang bcas pa'i sgrub lugs phul lo //
NK036(chi)030:437: dge'u gong du bzhugs dus gu ru zhi bas zhal gzigs /
NK036(chi)030:438: mkha' spyod du byon nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis chos 'chad lugs rnam thar rnams gzigs shing /
NK036(chi)030:439: bkra shis me tog 'thor ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:440: 'byon dus mkha' 'gro ma rnas kyis skyel thung byas te /
NK036(chi)030:441: mkha' 'gro snying thig gi rjes gnang phul lo //
NK036(chi)030:442: dge 'ur bzhugs dus phag mo dmar mo dang /
NK036(chi)030:446: tshe dpag med bzhengs stabs rnams 'od dkyil nas zhal gzigs so //
NK036(chi)030:447: dur khrod du bzhugs dus las kyi mkha' 'gro ma e ka tsa ti spyan gcig ma /
NK036(chi)030:448: spyang mo zhing dbyug can mthing mo /
NK036(chi)030:450: rdo rje legs pa rnams gzigs so //
NK036(chi)030:451: bya 'ug lha khang du mgon po phyag bzhi pa /
NK036(chi)030:453: dge bsnyen nyer gcig gzigs so //
NK036(chi)030:454: chos khams dge ba rgya mtsho'i gos can gzhir //
NK036(chi)030:455: byang chub sems mchog bzang po'i sa lud bran //
NK036(chi)030:456: smon dang 'jug pa'i sa bon legs btab nas //
NK036(chi)030:457: dge bcu'i lo thog gsar du smin mdzad bstod //
NK036(chi)030:458: de'i dpyid sor jo bo mjal du byon pas jo
NK036(chi)030:459: bo'i mdzod spu nas 'od zer spros pa nyid kyi
NK036(chi)030:461: bya rgod phung po'i ri dang /
NK036(chi)030:463: pan+di ta ma h+aa mu tra bya bar sku 'khrungs pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:464: rgya gar du mkhyen pa'i chos gsar rnying la sogs pa thugs la bkra lam pa zhig gsal bas /
NK036(chi)030:465: sngar bas thugs rtag tu bde ba zhig byung /
NK036(chi)030:466: dan phag tu byon nas gsang snying gsan te mar lam res mo dgon par byon nas /
NK036(chi)030:467: bla ma res mo ba dang gsung gleng mdzad par /
NK036(chi)030:468: bud med nag mo gcig gis po ti gcig khyer byung nas gzig pas /
NK036(chi)030:469: d+aak+ki tsit+ta bya ba gcig 'dug de'i 'phro la mi snang bar gyur to //
NK036(chi)030:470: de la bla ma res mo ngo mtshar skyes nas chos zhus pas /
NK036(chi)030:471: mchims phur snying thig gsang ba'i zhal bzhes mdzad nas byon no //
NK036(chi)030:472: dgung lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad bzhes pa 'bri khung
NK036(chi)030:473: chos rje chos kyi rgyal po sku 'khrungs pa dang
NK036(chi)030:474: dus mtshungs pa med pa me phag lo yin nam
NK036(chi)030:475: dpyad dgos / mthong snang 'od dra las dgung lo
NK036(chi)030:476: so gnyis la gsungs pa mdzad 'dug de ltar na
NK036(chi)030:478: la ri mo can du snying thig gsungs pas chos 'dzugs pa'i sar me tog gi char babs /
NK036(chi)030:479: spros bcas kyi tshe 'od mthing kas thams cad brdal bar khyab cing /
NK036(chi)030:480: spros med kyi dgong mo 'od zer kha dog lngas khyab cing /
NK036(chi)030:481: o rgyan sku mdog mthing kha dang /
NK036(chi)030:482: ye shes mtsho rgyal dmar mo phyag na bum pa bsnams nas /
NK036(chi)030:483: khong rang la dbang bskur dus nam mkha' las 'od dang /
NK036(chi)030:486: ngo mtshar ba mang po byung zhing /
NK036(chi)030:487: dkyil 'khor gyi rtsar bu mo lo bcu drug tsam g.yu ltar sngo ba bdun byung nas /
NK036(chi)030:488: bro 'khrab pas ched du dgyes pa dang mi dgyes pa la sogs pa ma mdzad gsung /
NK036(chi)030:489: 'di'i dus su o rgyan yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas mkha' 'gro snying thig gi rjes gnang /
NK036(chi)030:490: lha ring brag dang o rgyan rdzong dang /
NK036(chi)030:491: zhwa'i lha khang gso dgos pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:492: bstan bcos rtsom pa'i lung bstan yang thob /
NK036(chi)030:493: mtshan yang o rgyan gyis dri med 'od zer btags /
NK036(chi)030:494: ye shes mtsho rgyal gyis rdo rje gzi brjid ces gsol lo //
NK036(chi)030:495: de yang a ti bkod pa chen po dang /
NK036(chi)030:496: sgra thal 'gyur rtsa ba'i rgyud nas /
NK036(chi)030:498: zhes pa ni chos rje rin po cher bzhed /
NK036(chi)030:500: blo gros ming can thogs med bya bzhin rgyu //
NK036(chi)030:502: skyes bu 'di ni 'phags chen mchog la dbang //
NK036(chi)030:503: rgyal bas lung bstan chos bdag rnams kyis bstod //
NK036(chi)030:504: mkha' 'gro rnams kyis zab gter bdag por bskos //
NK036(chi)030:505: 'di 'dra'i mkhas grub dam pa gzhan su zhig /
NK036(chi)030:506: de nas gangs ri thod dkar gyi mgul du byon
NK036(chi)030:507: nas bstan ma bcu gnyis lha rabs mched dgu rnams
NK036(chi)030:508: kyis bsu ba mdzad pa'i snang ba byung ngo //
NK036(chi)030:509: lo gsum sgrub pa mdzad cing bzhugs dus /
NK036(chi)030:510: tho rangs kha gcig rmi lam na bla ma ku
NK036(chi)030:511: ma r+aa dza byon nas sdigs mdzub gcig mdzad de
NK036(chi)030:512: / ci yang mi gsungs pas dbang gi brda ru go ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:514: ting nge 'dzin gcig gis tshe 'phel ba yin gsung /
NK036(chi)030:515: de'i nyi ma rtse shar la mngon sum gzigs dus /
NK036(chi)030:516: shar phyogs kyi nam mkha' las sgra zhig grags pa /
NK036(chi)030:517: de'i dus nam mkhar gzigs pas /
NK036(chi)030:518: 'od kyi dkyil 'khor tshom bu dang bcas pa'i dkyil du kun bzang yab yum dang /
NK036(chi)030:519: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor mang po sa gzhi bar snang steng 'og phyogs mtshams gang bar gzigs pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:520: bi ma la sku mdog ljang ser dang mkha' spyod kyi bla ma bzhi /
NK036(chi)030:521: bla ma ku ma r+aa dza longs spyod rdzogs pa'i cha byad dang /
NK036(chi)030:522: o rgyan pad+ma rgyal po'i cha byad can gzigs pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:523: de nas bzung ste lha'i zhal mang po rgyun chad med par gzigs gsung /
NK036(chi)030:524: de nas bod kyi ri bo rtse lngar byon dus
NK036(chi)030:525: 'ja' dang 'od kyi gur mang po phub nas ya
NK036(chi)030:526: mtshan gyi rtags mang po byung zhing /
NK036(chi)030:527: sgyu 'phrul skor gyi cho ga mdzad pas zhi khro'i
NK036(chi)030:528: dkyil 'khor nam mkha' dang brag la sogs pa thams
NK036(chi)030:529: cad du tshom bu gsal bar kun gyis mthong ba
NK036(chi)030:530: dang / dar cig snang ba 'gyur nas /
NK036(chi)030:531: shar lho'i mtshams su gzigs pas /
NK036(chi)030:532: nam mkhar bi ma la bzhugs nas phyag mdzub shar lho mtshams su bstan pa gzigs pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:533: lha khang gso ba'i sngar gyi lung bstan rjes su dran no //
NK036(chi)030:534: de lta'i skyes bu khyu mchog de'i yon tan brjod pa /
NK036(chi)030:535: khrom nas chos bshad gang+g+aa'i chu rgyun 'dra //
NK036(chi)030:536: rig grwar rtsod dus 'brug sgra sgrogs pa 'dra //
NK036(chi)030:537: bstan bcos rtsoms dus ri gzar 'bab chu 'dra //
NK036(chi)030:538: mnyam par 'jog dus rnal 'byor mngon sum 'dra //
NK036(chi)030:539: zhes pa'i don la gnas pa'o //
NK036(chi)030:541: o rgyan gyi slob dpon gyis /
NK036(chi)030:542: 'bri gung sgom pa kun rin la //
NK036(chi)030:543: 'bri zhes bya ba'i sa phyogs su //
NK036(chi)030:544: kun dag'i ming can bdud kyi bu //
NK036(chi)030:545: lus la mtshon cha'i ri mo yod //
NK036(chi)030:546: shi nas dmyal bar skye bar 'gyur //
NK036(chi)030:547: lho yi phyogs nas 'jam dbyangs kyi //
NK036(chi)030:548: sprul pa gcig gis thul gyur na //
NK036(chi)030:549: mnar med gnas nas thar bar 'gyur //
NK036(chi)030:550: zhes pa de sgom pa kun rin gyis mthong ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:551: lus la bltas pas rgyab kyi sgal gzhung g.yas su
NK036(chi)030:552: ral gri 'dra ba'i sha mtshan cig 'dug pas ngas
NK036(chi)030:553: dbus gtsang 'khrugs pa zhig bya dgos bsam pa yod
NK036(chi)030:554: kyang / dmyal bar 'gro na byed don chung bas /
NK036(chi)030:555: bla ma dpal mchog pa la 'jam dbyangs kyi sprul
NK036(chi)030:556: pa gcig 'tshol la shog ngas chos zhu ba yin
NK036(chi)030:557: gsungs pa dang / bla ma dpal mchog pas dbus gtsang du 'tshol du byon pas /
NK036(chi)030:558: dbus gtsang na bla ma rgyal sras pa las thugs rab che ba mi 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)030:559: sgom pa kun rin la kun mkhyen pa gdan drang byas pas /
NK036(chi)030:560: khyed dad pa skyes pa na nga dad pa skye ba yin pas de ltar bya'o gsungs so //
NK036(chi)030:561: de nas 'bri gung du 'byon par zhal bzhes mdzad dus /
NK036(chi)030:562: mnal lam du seng ge bzhi'i khri'i steng na bi
NK036(chi)030:563: ma la bzhugs nas nga ni ku ma r+aa dza'i
NK036(chi)030:564: sprul pa yin / pad+ma brtsegs pa'i zhing du 'gro
NK036(chi)030:565: sangs rgyas kyi bstan par dar bar gyis shig gsungs
NK036(chi)030:566: sprul pa yin / / yang de'i sang dgongs phag mo lcags gdong ma /
NK036(chi)030:567: khong gi gzims sa'i mdun gyi rgya mthongs khar byon pa /
NK036(chi)030:568: bla ma ku ma r+aa dza'i sprul pa yin par mkhyen pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:569: yang bstan pa'i gnyer gtad do //
NK036(chi)030:570: 'di'i dus su mya ngan 'das chung mdzad do //
NK036(chi)030:571: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa lan gnyis su /
NK036(chi)030:572: 'bul ba lnga dang bdun gyis bla ma'i gshegs rdzong mdzad kyang /
NK036(chi)030:573: bla ma'i phyi rten nang rten la 'od gsal snying
NK036(chi)030:574: po'i bstan pa mi nub par bya ba'i phyir du
NK036(chi)030:575: / theg mchog rin po che'i mdzod brtsams pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:576: de dus sngags bdag gza' dang dam can rnams dang
NK036(chi)030:577: dngos su mi dang mi lab pa bzhin byung ba
NK036(chi)030:578: dang / las sgrub pa dang lung bstan pa dang bka' srung ba la sogs pa yang mdzad do //
NK036(chi)030:579: ji ltar mtshan mo dwangs pa'i nam mkha' las //
NK036(chi)030:580: ri bong 'dzin pa shar bar ku mu ta //
NK036(chi)030:581: dgod pa bzhin du kha bye lhag ger gsal //
NK036(chi)030:582: zhar la rgyu skar tshogs rnams dman par gyur //
NK036(chi)030:583: snyigs ma'i dus 'dir 'jam dbyangs sprul pa mchog /
NK036(chi)030:584: kun mkhyen byon pas skal ldan mchog tu rgyal //
NK036(chi)030:585: zhar la bla ma'i gzugs brnyan rnams kyang nyams //
NK036(chi)030:586: yon tan mchog gis dman rnams zil gyis gnon //
NK036(chi)030:587: de ltar sngar bsam yas su bzhugs dus ya bo
NK036(chi)030:588: dbang rgyal zhes bya bas gdan drangs nas zhag bdun
NK036(chi)030:589: du kun rig gi dbang zhus /
NK036(chi)030:590: snying tig gi khrid zhus pa'i snga shos glu mkhan pa bsod nams seng ges byas /
NK036(chi)030:591: phyogs kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen 'dus pa rnams kyi
NK036(chi)030:592: snga shos slob dpon gzhon nu sangs rgyas kyis byas
NK036(chi)030:593: te / yon bdag la snga shos ya bo dbang rgyal /
NK036(chi)030:594: bu slob kyi snga shos glu mkhan pa bsod nams seng ge /
NK036(chi)030:595: dge ba'i bshes gnyen 'du ba'i snga shos slob dpon dpal mchog ces bya bar grags shing /
NK036(chi)030:596: rgya ma ba dkon gnyer gyis glu mkhan bsod nams seng ge la /
NK036(chi)030:597: khyod kyis ma bskor ba'i sa cha med pas rdzogs chen la su mkhas par 'dug /
NK036(chi)030:598: ngas zhu 'dod pa yin zhes zer ba la /
NK036(chi)030:599: ngas dbus gtsang gi bla ma ma mjal ba med /
NK036(chi)030:600: rdzogs chen pa yang mang po snang ste /
NK036(chi)030:601: nged rang dang nye ba'i sa phyogs zhig na yongs
NK036(chi)030:602: kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen khyad par du rdzogs pa
NK036(chi)030:603: chen po la mkhas pa gcig bzhugs zer bas /
NK036(chi)030:604: khong gdan 'dren pa la btang nas rgya ma'i gnas su gdan drangs /
NK036(chi)030:605: rgya ma sgang pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen pa rnams dang /
NK036(chi)030:606: dkon gnyer gyis snying tig zhus pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)030:607: khong rnams dri ba la rgyugs nas bgro gleng byas par zhus pas /
NK036(chi)030:609: rig grwa sogs zla ba gcig gi bar du khyed rnams la rtsod rgyu yod pa yin /
NK036(chi)030:610: zhag bcu tsam gyi bar du mdo rgyud dpang por
NK036(chi)030:611: bzhag nas lung rig gi rtsod pa byed gsungs pas
NK036(chi)030:612: / khong rnams spobs pa med par gyur nas nged rnams kyis ma go bar 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)030:613: chos thugs la 'dog par zhu zer zhing thams cad 'dun par gyur /
NK036(chi)030:614: dbus stod du sgom pa kun rin gyis gdan drangs nas /
NK036(chi)030:615: byon pa dang grog gi mdar phyags phebs dus /
NK036(chi)030:616: ti sgro'i las kyi d+aak+kisa bsu ba mdzad cing o rgyan dgon pa phul lo //
NK036(chi)030:617: de nas zhwa'i lha khang du byon dus /
NK036(chi)030:618: mi dkar po zhwa dkar po can cig byung nas zhwa phud de phyag byas shing /
NK036(chi)030:619: zhwa'i lha khang la sdigs mdzub gcig mdzad dgung lo
NK036(chi)030:620: zhe gnyis bzhes pa sa mo glang gi lo yin
NK036(chi)030:621: bya ba rtsis kyi yi ge zhib mor bris 'dug
NK036(chi)030:623: tshes bcu'i dus su mkha' 'gro 'du tshogs mang bar gzigs so //
NK036(chi)030:624: de nas zhwa'i lha khang gsol dus dbu rtse'i rgyab nas gser 'gu tshe gang bcus nas /
NK036(chi)030:625: gtsug lag khang bzhengs pa'i cha rkyen dang lha rnams kyi sku gser byas /
NK036(chi)030:626: gter kha mang bar 'dug kyang rgya mthongs 'og nas sngags bag re tsam dang /
NK036(chi)030:629: bstan ma bcu gnyis kyi sgrub thabs dang /
NK036(chi)030:630: dam can gyi sgrub thabs tsam las gzhan ma blangs gsungs /
NK036(chi)030:631: sa rdo bsal dus mnan pa'i thod pa mang po 'phar zhing byung ba /
NK036(chi)030:632: na bza' g.yab pas bzung zhing slar gnon pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:633: de'i dus legs nyes kyi gtam mi dgos gza' dang rdo rje legs pas mang du bshad pa byung /
NK036(chi)030:634: nyin bzhin du bu tsha g.yu rna can lo brgyad pa tsam zhig /
NK036(chi)030:635: gzo rig pa rnams kyi rtsar slebs nas gro'i skabs
NK036(chi)030:636: su gar song cha med la 'gro yin 'dug par
NK036(chi)030:637: / thams cad kyis ci yin bgros te sang nyin
NK036(chi)030:638: gro'i dus na gar song blta dgos zhes thams cad
NK036(chi)030:640: gro la 'gro ba'i dus su bsrungs pas /
NK036(chi)030:641: rtsig pa'i gseb tu thim nas gar song cha med /
NK036(chi)030:642: 'di na dpal ldan bla ma dam pa'i thugs rjes
NK036(chi)030:643: gtsug lag khang bzhengs pa'i stong grogs dam can rdo
NK036(chi)030:644: rje legs pas mdzad par mngon no //
NK036(chi)030:645: lung pa nas brag la brkos pa'i rdo ring chen po mnyam pa gnyis yod pa la /
NK036(chi)030:646: gcig cung zad chag nas gnyis ka la zhwa'i sa
NK036(chi)030:647: cha'i thob rigs gzong gis brkos nas yod pa las
NK036(chi)030:648: / phyis gtsug lag khang bzhengs dus rtsa ba 'gyel pa la song nas /
NK036(chi)030:650: mi lag gdangs pa'i thag 'gyogs 'debs pa'i 'phrul ci byas kyang bslangs ma nus /
NK036(chi)030:651: chos rje nyid kyis gtor ma zhig mdzad bden pa'i tshig brjod nas /
NK036(chi)030:652: sku chos kyi g.yab mo brdul bas rdo ring bsrangs par gyur te /
NK036(chi)030:653: ngo mtshar ba'i cho 'phrul du bstan /
NK036(chi)030:654: de nas mtha' dmag gi 'byung po thams cad yun
NK036(chi)030:655: ring du mnan nas sngar gyi mnan pa'i sems can
NK036(chi)030:656: rigs mi gcig pa mang po'i thod pa'i nang gi
NK036(chi)030:657: ling+ga gso dgos pa rnams gsos /
NK036(chi)030:658: mnan pa mdzad pa'i grab mdzad pa'i tshe sa rdo'i
NK036(chi)030:659: char babs rlung nag gi 'tshub ma g.yos te rtsub
NK036(chi)030:661: mi rnams skrag cing brgyal nas mnan pa byed pa'i grogs ma byung /
NK036(chi)030:662: chos rje pa nyid kyis he ru ka'i gar dang sam kri ta'i skad mang po mdzad pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)030:663: thod pa rnams sa las 'phar ba gcig la gcig brdabs pa'i skad byung /
NK036(chi)030:664: thod pa che shos gcig nam mkha' la 'phar zhing 'dug pa /
NK036(chi)030:666: gar dgu'i nyams dang ldan par mdzad pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)030:667: kun mkhyen bsod nams bzang pos gu ru drag po'i skur mthong nas /
NK036(chi)030:668: thod pa rnams phra men mchod rten gyi zhabs su gnan no //
NK036(chi)030:669: stobs chen 'di yi mdzad pa mtha' yas kyis //
NK036(chi)030:670: drag po'i 'dul la khro zhing gtum par ston //
NK036(chi)030:671: zhi ba'i 'dul la dgyes pa'i zhal bzang 'dzum //
NK036(chi)030:672: mdor na rdzu 'phrul cho 'phrul dpag tu med //
NK036(chi)030:673: de nas rab gnas mdzad pa'i dus su kun tu bzang po'iskura gyur nas 'dug pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:674: thugs ka nas 'od zer mang po 'phros pa las /
NK036(chi)030:675: 'od zer re re'i rtse la sangs rgyas byang chub
NK036(chi)030:676: sems dpa' grangs med pa bzhugs pa las can gyi
NK036(chi)030:677: slob ma 'ga' yis mthong ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:678: la stod dbang rin bya bas me tog thams cad
NK036(chi)030:679: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpas gtor ba yang
NK036(chi)030:680: mthong ngo // khong rang gi thugs nyams la /
NK036(chi)030:683: gnas brtan bcu drug rnams zhal 'dzum lhag lhag mthong gsung ngo //
NK036(chi)030:684: byams pas phyag mdzub gdengs nas lung bstan pa /
NK036(chi)030:685: khyed skye ba gnyis 'das pa'i 'og tu /
NK036(chi)030:686: pad+ma brtsegs pa'i zhing du byang chub sems dpa' ri
NK036(chi)030:687: rab mar me'i rgyal ma tshan zhes bya bar 'gyur
NK036(chi)030:688: ro // zhes gsungs pa'i lung bstan thob bo //
NK036(chi)030:689: skye ba sngon nas rgyal ba rgya mtsho la //
NK036(chi)030:690: tshogs chen rab bsags lhag par mnyes bgyis pas //
NK036(chi)030:691: tshe 'dir sangs rgyas bstan pa'i khur khyer nas //
NK036(chi)030:692: rgyal bas lung bstan mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK036(chi)030:693: spre'u lo'i tshes bcu mdzad pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)030:694: nam mkha' 'od phung gi dkyil du o rgyan sku
NK036(chi)030:695: mdog dkar po d+aak+ki sde lngas bskor ba las 'od
NK036(chi)030:697: mi khri bzhi stong 'dus pa las /
NK036(chi)030:698: ti sgro'i mkha' 'gro ma rnams der lhags nas /
NK036(chi)030:699: mkha' 'gro babs pa bcu phrag lnga bcu byung nas legs nyes thams cad smra ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:700: mon bum thang du 'byon par yang lung bstan no //
NK036(chi)030:701: der zhwa pad+ma dbang chen gyi rab gnas tshar nas /
NK036(chi)030:702: ti sgro la byon nas zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK036(chi)030:703: gi bar du zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs nas bskang
NK036(chi)030:705: bar skabs su ma jo gnyis dam sel byas pas gnas de nyams 'dug pa gsos /
NK036(chi)030:706: mis mi thar pa'i brag la chos rje nyid kyis rgyal mtshan dang cod pan btsugs so //
NK036(chi)030:707: de nas shugs gseb tu byon nas bzhugs dus /
NK036(chi)030:708: gsal snang gcig la jo mo kha rag gi rgyab
NK036(chi)030:709: nas lus po med pa'i khro bo'i mgo bo ri
NK036(chi)030:711: kha nas glo 'khyugs pa zhig 'dug pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:712: yar klungs zo thang gong po ri nas /
NK036(chi)030:713: de las che ba'i mgo bo nag po gcig byung nas mig 'phrul zhing kha nas 'od 'phro bas /
NK036(chi)030:714: 'od de jo mo kha rag gi mgo de'i thad nas yar song ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:715: kha rag gi mgo bo de med par 'od de la stod nas yal song bas /
NK036(chi)030:716: bod khams kun ser ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:720: dus mi bde ba yong mthar 'bros pa yin gsungs nas /
NK036(chi)030:721: yer pa la so nam zhig bya bsam pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:722: lha sar ma ni'i khang bu zhig brtsig bsams pa yin te /
NK036(chi)030:723: da res mi 'grub par gda' bas /
NK036(chi)030:724: nged rang dpon slob tsho bum thang du 'gro gsungs nas zhal ta mang du mdzad do //
NK036(chi)030:725: dbus gtsang 'di na nad mug mtshon gsum dar //
NK036(chi)030:726: 'di 'dra'i sa char sdod pa mi rig pas //
NK036(chi)030:727: lung bstan bzhin du glo mon 'dul bar dgongs //
NK036(chi)030:728: dus gsum rnam mkhyen de la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)030:729: de nas lha sar byon dus /
NK036(chi)030:730: 'di 'bri gung pa'i rtsa ba'i bla ma yin zer nas /
NK036(chi)030:731: yar klung pas bkrong ba'i rtsis byas dmag gis bskor
NK036(chi)030:732: nas bkrong par brtsams pa la thun mong gi dngos
NK036(chi)030:733: grub brgyad kyi ya gyal mi snang ba'i rdzu 'phrul
NK036(chi)030:734: mdzad pas / btsal byung zhing ma mthong nas /
NK036(chi)030:735: der bros nas mi 'dug zer zhing //
NK036(chi)030:736: khong rnams kyis glags ma rnyed do //
NK036(chi)030:737: skyes chen 'di ni dngos grub gzugs sprin che //
NK036(chi)030:738: rdzu 'phrul thogs med chos skyong las rnams bsgrubs //
NK036(chi)030:739: de 'dra'i mdzad spyod su yis 'gran par nus //
NK036(chi)030:740: rtsod med grub chen de la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)030:741: lha sa'i bar khang na bzhugs pa'i mtshan mo jo bo'i mdun du bzhugs pa las /
NK036(chi)030:742: jo bo'i sku las gser lta bu'i 'od zer 'phro ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:743: jo bo'i dbu'i steng na 'od kyi nang na sangs rgyas rabs bdun /
NK036(chi)030:748: spyan ras gzigs rgyal po lugs /
NK036(chi)030:750: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams kyi mtha' na /
NK036(chi)030:751: mgon po ber nag can dang /
NK036(chi)030:754: dpal ldan lha mo rnams bzhengs nas /
NK036(chi)030:755: nam mkhar gzigs shing 'dug pa gzigs so //
NK036(chi)030:756: de'i nyin par brag lha klu phug tu byon nas /
NK036(chi)030:757: nyin dang mtshan du rin po che gcig thugs la wal wa la byung nas /
NK036(chi)030:758: mtshan mo mnal lam du gangs ti se dang /
NK036(chi)030:759: ts+aa ri shel ri rnams su byon nas legs par gzigs pa zhig rmis gsung /
NK036(chi)030:760: de nas lho ru byon dus /
NK036(chi)030:761: pho ma skyong thang du dge bsnyen nyer gcig dang /
NK036(chi)030:763: spyan gzigs drangs pa yang byung /
NK036(chi)030:764: yang bum thang du byon dus dge bsnyen nyer gcig gis bsu ba byas /
NK036(chi)030:767: skyes mchog dam pa mi yi seng+ge des //
NK036(chi)030:768: sangs rgyas bstan la ston pa'i bya ba mdzad //
NK036(chi)030:770: thar lam ston mdzad de la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)030:771: gzhan yang gdul bar dka' ba'i phyogs glo mon dge sdig mi shes shing /
NK036(chi)030:772: gsod gcod la dga' ba chos ma dar ba'i sa phyogs rnams su yang /
NK036(chi)030:773: 'gro ba sems can rnams rjes su 'dzin pa'i slad du /
NK036(chi)030:774: mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams kyis de dag zil gyis mnan nas /
NK036(chi)030:778: thams cad bde 'jam gyi lam la bkod de /
NK036(chi)030:779: byang chub kyi sa bon thebs par mdzad do //
NK036(chi)030:780: byams pa lha khang du phyag phebs pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:781: thar pa'i gling du gzigs pas /
NK036(chi)030:782: ri rtse la 'od kyi 'khor lo zhig gzigs /
NK036(chi)030:783: thar pa'i gling du bzhugs dus /
NK036(chi)030:784: lho phyogs kyi mtsho nag po gcig gi nang nas /
NK036(chi)030:785: g.yag rog po gcig thon byung bas /
NK036(chi)030:786: ri bo 'degs pa dang du ba 'thul ba la sogs pa'i cho 'phrul byung bas /
NK036(chi)030:787: sa 'dul ba'i rten 'brel mang po mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:788: mon bum thang chos kyi sgra mi grags pa'i sa rnams su /
NK036(chi)030:789: tshogs pa 'bum phrag 'du ba'i dge 'dun gyi sde btsugs te thar pa gling du ming btags /
NK036(chi)030:790: slob dpon dpal mchog gi gcung po /
NK036(chi)030:791: slob dpon sangs rgyas kun dga' zhes bya ba bla mar bskos /
NK036(chi)030:792: thams cad dam pa'i chos rdzogs pa chen po'i lta sgom la bkod do //
NK036(chi)030:793: mngon par rdzogs sangs rgyas kyang bshes gnyen mchog tu bsten //
NK036(chi)030:794: spangs rtogs phun sum tshogs kyang sems can don la brtson //
NK036(chi)030:795: rang don chos sku brnyes kyang gzhan don gzugs sku'i mdzod //
NK036(chi)030:796: sngon med nam mkha'i nor bu de ni gtsug gis mchod //
NK036(chi)030:798: yar 'brog pa la sogs pas gdan 'dren byung nas /
NK036(chi)030:800: mkhan chen dge 'dun rgyal mtshan gyi zhabs su dge 'dun lnga brgya 'du ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:801: bla ma spus gong pa la dge 'dun sum brgya
NK036(chi)030:802: lhag 'dus pa rnams la 'od gsal rdo rje snying
NK036(chi)030:803: po'i khrid bstan nas smin grol la bkod do //
NK036(chi)030:804: de nas khrid dpon rdo rjee rgyal mtshan pas gdan drangs nas yar 'brog tu chos gsung dus /
NK036(chi)030:805: dbur stod nas bla ma o rgyan pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:806: rgyal sras bzod pa dge slong gzhon nu bkra shis la sogs pa rnams mjal du byon /
NK036(chi)030:807: dbus su 'byon pa'i zhu ba byas /
NK036(chi)030:810: do dgongs nga'i cha ther 'og tu shog /
NK036(chi)030:811: do nub lhan du sdod pa yin gsung /
NK036(chi)030:812: der byon pas gsol ja ba chos dpal rgyal mtshan la /
NK036(chi)030:813: nged dpon slob la zas sna bzang po gyis la drongs /
NK036(chi)030:814: ja bzang po gcig kyang bkol gsung nas dgyes tshor chen po mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:817: khri dpon rdo rje rgyam tshan gyis mkha' 'gro snying
NK036(chi)030:818: tig gi zhu ba byas pas bshad par byas nas
NK036(chi)030:819: yod / khyod mkha' 'gro snying thig 'tshol ba la
NK036(chi)030:820: kong por chos rgyal rin chen gling pa'i rtsar 'gro
NK036(chi)030:822: de ltar gyis byas nas btang ba yin /
NK036(chi)030:823: kong po na rin chen gling pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:824: dwags po byar na gter ston gyi dngos slob sprul sku legs ldan pa gnyis la /
NK036(chi)030:825: mkha' 'gro snying thig zhus nas 'dug pa legs /
NK036(chi)030:826: da gdod rgyud dag ma dag gi gtam mi yong ba yin /
NK036(chi)030:827: don dam par chos 'di'i bdag po nga yin /
NK036(chi)030:828: nyams snang dang rmi lam la chos 'di'i bdag po khyod yin gsung ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:829: dngos su chos bdag gi mkha' 'gro rnams kyis mngon sum du nga la gtad pa yin /
NK036(chi)030:830: khyod rang rings rgyu med na sdod la chos 'di nyon /
NK036(chi)030:832: glu gang mkhas bro rar bcug na gsal bya ba yin pas /
NK036(chi)030:833: khong gnyis dang gang mkhas yid ches skye ba yin gsung /
NK036(chi)030:834: rgyal sras rin po ches bla ma o rgyan pa
NK036(chi)030:835: la mkha' 'gro snying thig gsung pa 'dra bas khyed
NK036(chi)030:838: bi ma snying thig tshar mang zhig thob /
NK036(chi)030:839: mkha' 'gro snying thig la yang de las lhag pa med las che nged 'gro ba yin gsung /
NK036(chi)030:840: 'o na de ltar mdzod byas khong rnams bzhud /
NK036(chi)030:841: 'brog khri dpon pas gtso mdzad dpon g.yog bcu gsum dge slong dpal 'byor bcas bsdad pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:842: bla ma dang dpon slob yongs dril dpon g.yog bco lnga la mkha' 'gro snying thig gi khrid gsung /
NK036(chi)030:843: gter nas byon 'phral mkha' 'gro'i kha rlangs thu le ba'i chos yin pas dam dogs che bar mdzod /
NK036(chi)030:844: kun tu bzang po sangs rgyas mi gzugs can //
NK036(chi)030:845: chos mchog zab gter mkha' 'gro snying thig ste //
NK036(chi)030:846: sras kyi thu bo rgyal sras bzod pa la //
NK036(chi)030:847: thugs kyi dkyil du dgongs pas dgyes par gnang //
NK036(chi)030:848: bsnyel ba mi mnga' thugs rje'i bdag nyid can //
NK036(chi)030:849: khyed kyi rjes 'jug rnams la thar pa'i lam //
NK036(chi)030:850: tshe gcig sangs rgyas lag tu gtod mdzad pa'i //
NK036(chi)030:851: bshes gnyen dam pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK036(chi)030:852: de nas g.yor po gzhung du gdan drangs pa la sngar dgrar 'dzin cing yod na'ang /
NK036(chi)030:853: mdzad pa dang 'du ba la dad par gyur nas
NK036(chi)030:854: t+aa'i si tu byang chub rgyal mtshan gyis sngon la
NK036(chi)030:855: ja 'dren / rting la ja sig gcig /
NK036(chi)030:857: de'i sha mar thud rnams phog btab /
NK036(chi)030:858: na bza' cha tshang gcig 'bul bar byas /
NK036(chi)030:859: de nas snyan pa dang grags pa dang gdul bya che zhing /
NK036(chi)030:860: 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i yon tan la dad de /
NK036(chi)030:861: sangs rgyas dpal rin gyis dpon slob kyi mtshams sbyar /
NK036(chi)030:863: si tu pas gtso mdzad rnams la o rgyan nag
NK036(chi)030:864: po'i dbang dang byin rlabs gnang bas mos pa thob
NK036(chi)030:865: ste / rjes gshegs pa'i rjes su'ang gdung 'bul gyis mnyes par byas pa'o //
NK036(chi)030:866: de nas khrid btsugs te stong phrag yod zer ba'i tshogs pa 'dus /
NK036(chi)030:867: dbur stod nas kyang bla ma dam pa rgyal sras bzod pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:868: dge slong grags pa dpal gyis thog drangs chos nyan mang rabs chos gsan du byon /
NK036(chi)030:869: tshogs pa ches pos chos nyan la phyag dam 'gyed dgos pa byung /
NK036(chi)030:870: der tshogs pa rnams smin grol gyi lam la bkod /
NK036(chi)030:871: de'i dus su chos rje bla ma rgyal mtshan dam pa'i drung nas /
NK036(chi)030:872: 'phan yul ba'i slob ma thun mong ba zhig la /
NK036(chi)030:873: bla ma dam pa rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhi lam
NK036(chi)030:874: 'bras bu'i bzhed tshul ci 'dra ba yin zhus pa
NK036(chi)030:875: las / gzhi lam 'bras bu'i bzhed tshul tshig nyung
NK036(chi)030:876: la don 'gril ba zhig rin po che gser gyi
NK036(chi)030:877: mchod sdong zhes bya ba tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs
NK036(chi)030:878: kyis phul ba'i rgyab yig las /
NK036(chi)030:879: rab gsal snyan par smra ba'i ngag 'di ni //
NK036(chi)030:880: 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i gnas la ma rmongs shing //
NK036(chi)030:881: lung rig man ngag du ma'i blo mig can //
NK036(chi)030:882: snying po'i de nyid rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK036(chi)030:883: gzhung ri rin chen brtsegs pa'i gnas nas phul //
NK036(chi)030:884: ces pa'i zhu yig phyag tu phul bas /
NK036(chi)030:885: chos rje bsod rgyal ba bsam yas su bzhugs pas /
NK036(chi)030:886: chos rje ngor du phyag thegs pa'i shul /
NK036(chi)030:887: gzims chung gi glo phug tu lus nas 'dug pa bsam yas kyi dkor gnyer des /
NK036(chi)030:888: rdzogs chen pa'i sgom chen gcig la khyed kyi bla ma rdzogs chen pa'i gsung sgros zhig /
NK036(chi)030:889: chos rje bsod rgyal ba phyag thegs pa'i gzims chung du lus nas 'dug zer bas /
NK036(chi)030:890: de nga la e ster byas pas chog zer nas byin /
NK036(chi)030:891: do red sa rtsa smag dus sgo drag po brdung zhing 'dug pa bltas pas /
NK036(chi)030:892: dkor gnyer des sbyin pas chog le ma red /
NK036(chi)030:893: gsung shog mdzad nas nye gnas len du btang 'dug pa la da lta rang skur gsung /
NK036(chi)030:894: skyil smad pa'i zul phu ba ston grags kyis khrid gzhi la nas khal sum brgya phul /
NK036(chi)030:895: skyor mo lung pa des nas khal nyis brgya 'bul zer ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:896: gzhan yang brgya 'bul ba kha yar byung /
NK036(chi)030:897: de dus dbus stod nas t+aa'i si tu sh+aakya bzang pos thog drangs /
NK036(chi)030:898: slob ma rnams kyis gdan 'dren yang byung /
NK036(chi)030:899: skabs shig la zhu ba nan ches pas 'byon par mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:900: phyag 'jog kha rang du gzhung nas kun mkhyen pa'i
NK036(chi)030:901: slob ma sngar mtshan nyid po ti 'ga' yang shes
NK036(chi)030:902: pa gcig gis drung du nga rang mjal nas chos
NK036(chi)030:903: zhu ba mang tshad yod na'ang /
NK036(chi)030:904: lo bdun du mtshams kyi dam bca' byas yod pas yong ba'i thabs ma byung /
NK036(chi)030:905: chos kyi dri ba 'di rnams kyi lan gsal po thugs la 'dogs pa zhu zer nas /
NK036(chi)030:906: zhu yig dang 'bul ba byung nas /
NK036(chi)030:907: nyin par ni chos dang mjal mkhan gyis brel bas thugs ma skabs /
NK036(chi)030:908: nub mo bla ma dam pa bzod pas /
NK036(chi)030:910: dris lan don gyi rab 'byed ces bya ba bskur /
NK036(chi)030:911: de nas byon pas lam du zhabs tog pa ma nga bas zhag sbrel 'gor /
NK036(chi)030:912: tshu ri pha ri rnams su skyel bsu ba ni tsho 'khrugs /
NK036(chi)030:913: tshur ri'i gtsang 'gram na chos khri brtsegs nas gsang
NK036(chi)030:914: phu gling stod pa'i slob dpon ye rgyal gyis thab
NK036(chi)030:915: khyogs nas ja gsol ba'i ring la /
NK036(chi)030:916: chos kyi dri ba tshig re zhus pa la mda' tshad mang rabs re'i lan gsung /
NK036(chi)030:917: des nas chos kyi drii ba zhu ba'i spobs pa
NK036(chi)030:918: med par gsang phu ba la nged rang 'dra ba
NK036(chi)030:919: gzhan med pas / skyong bran thugs la 'dogs par zhus /
NK036(chi)030:920: yang sgos su nged rang gling stod pa nyams nas yod zhus pas /
NK036(chi)030:921: khong la ja bzang po dum gcig /
NK036(chi)030:924: gling stod pa spyi la ja sig lnga /
NK036(chi)030:929: tshogs gnyis bsags pa'i 'bras bu dus 'dir smin //
NK036(chi)030:930: nam mkha' mdzod la mnga' brnyes phrin las can //
NK036(chi)030:931: sbyin pa rnam bzhis sems can tshim mdzad cing //
NK036(chi)030:932: re ba skong mdzad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK036(chi)030:933: de nas yar mo che ba'i jo gdan rnams kyis
NK036(chi)030:934: rol cha dang bcas lbu ba gdong nas bsu ba
NK036(chi)030:935: byas / ra mo cher phebs ja zhu zhing yod pa'i skabs su /
NK036(chi)030:936: rme ru ba'i jo gdan rnams mjal ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:937: ser sbrengs la byung ba la mjal kha ma byung /
NK036(chi)030:938: zla ba phyed ni lha sar bzhugs pa lha sa dang /
NK036(chi)030:939: ra sa gnyis kyi bar du khri mthon po brtsigs te thugs bskyed gsungs pas /
NK036(chi)030:940: sa phyogs de chos nyan gyis gang /
NK036(chi)030:941: gsang mtshur sde gsum gyi dge bshes nga rgyal can mang pos chos nyan sar ltad mo bltas pas /
NK036(chi)030:942: las rgyu 'bras kyi chos bshad mdzad pa'i rting na /
NK036(chi)030:943: khong rnams dad pa skyes nas /
NK036(chi)030:944: 'di 'dra zhig yin pa zer zhing phyag btsal te chos nyan gyi gral la 'khod /
NK036(chi)030:945: chos tshar nas ra mo cher 'byon zhing yod pa la /
NK036(chi)030:946: si tu sh+aakya bzang pos zhu yig dang gdan 'dren /
NK036(chi)030:947: gzhan yang bla ma dpon skya mang tshad gcig gis slebs nas byung /
NK036(chi)030:949: de nas snying thig gi khrid gsung pa la /
NK036(chi)030:950: snye phu shug gseb tu byon /
NK036(chi)030:951: khrid nyan stong phrag tshogs pas khrid zhu tsho 'di tsam mang 'dug pas /
NK036(chi)030:952: khrid gzhis mi lcogs par 'dug cing khrid gzhi rgyu khrid gnyer ba la 'bul bar zhu zhus pas /
NK036(chi)030:953: chos nyan rnams kyis mi lcogs na khas mi len pa yin zer ba la /
NK036(chi)030:954: chos rjee'i drung du khriid bzhi'i nas mang po phul bas mnyes pa che ba e yin /
NK036(chi)030:955: nga gar 'gro mkha' 'gro chos skyong gis bya ba sgrub cing yod pas /
NK036(chi)030:956: tshogs 'khor la mi thogs gsungs nas /
NK036(chi)030:957: phyag dam bkye nas chos gsung /
NK036(chi)030:958: dge slong dpon grags pas dbur stod du yar 'gro ba'i zhu ba byas pas /
NK036(chi)030:960: nga'i rta btsong nas med pas lha sa bar du chibs pa zhig g.yar po zhu zhus pas /
NK036(chi)030:961: rta med na khyed gar thon rta khyer bas chog gsung /
NK036(chi)030:962: nang par tsha ba gnang nas /
NK036(chi)030:963: chibs pa rngam pa sgra sgrogs btang /
NK036(chi)030:964: rta bsgyur ba la rtogs ldan gyad thung zer ba btang /
NK036(chi)030:965: lam ring thung gnyis yod pa'i thung ba des gzar bas ring ba de skor gsungs /
NK036(chi)030:966: phyag dbang zhus shing yod kyang ldabs nas gsungs /
NK036(chi)030:967: zhal ta'i lugs bzhin rtogs ldan gyis byed byas pas /
NK036(chi)030:969: ngas mi tshe rta la bskyal bas a'u tsi nye sa la 'gro byas pas /
NK036(chi)030:972: rtogs ldan rta bzlog nas 'gro dus /
NK036(chi)030:973: rtas brdabs pa ma zhu bka' bkyon thugs khrel yong zer nas ngag bsdams /
NK036(chi)030:974: shug gseb tu slebs dus chibs rta ka ba la gtod /
NK036(chi)030:975: drung du phyag 'tshal ba la song bas /
NK036(chi)030:976: ngan pa rnams byas pa la mi nyan de e ma byung /
NK036(chi)030:977: dge slong dpon grags par ra mo cher sman dpyad rim gro chen dgos pa byung /
NK036(chi)030:978: des na thogs pa med pa'i mngon par shes pa yod par yid ches so //
NK036(chi)030:979: mi yi khyu mchog chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK036(chi)030:980: smra ba'i zla ba mngon shes spyan dang ldan //
NK036(chi)030:981: 'phags pa'i gang zag 'di 'dra gzhan su zhig /
NK036(chi)030:982: dus gsum rnam mkhyen de la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)030:983: de nas dbur stod du byon nas /
NK036(chi)030:984: si tus mkhar ba ring gdan drangs /
NK036(chi)030:986: dbyar gnas kyi phog btab nas /
NK036(chi)030:988: tshogs pa rgya mtsho lta bu tshogs /
NK036(chi)030:989: o rgyan gyi rdza 'dabs man chad /
NK036(chi)030:990: pha ri'i brag rtsa de yan chad /
NK036(chi)030:991: cha theg dkar nag khra gsum gyis bkang /
NK036(chi)030:992: chos nyan rnyed pa las sum log gis mang /
NK036(chi)030:993: gsar pa'i chos nyan gyi drag pa dus 'khor ba dge 'dun dpal gyis thog drangs /
NK036(chi)030:994: chos 'chad pa'i bla ma slob dpon yang bzhi bcu la slebs tsam 'dug /
NK036(chi)030:995: 'bri gung pa'i khul gyi bla ma slob dpon /
NK036(chi)030:996: dpon skya mang po 'tshogs pa la /
NK036(chi)030:997: 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i khrid zla ba bzhi pa'i tshes bco lnga'i nyin par btsugs nas /
NK036(chi)030:998: tshes brgyad gcig la 'tshogs pa la 'gyed chen gcig mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:999: zla ba byung ngo cog gi tshes bcu la 'phan yul yan chad /
NK036(chi)030:1000: rtse mo rgyal phyin man chad tshogs pa rgya mtsho
NK036(chi)030:1001: lta bu la tshes bcu'i mchod pa gya nom pa
NK036(chi)030:1002: mdzad / sngar snying thig gi khrid zhu ba'i dus
NK036(chi)030:1003: chos khral la ma thogs pas da gzod nga la
NK036(chi)030:1004: chos bshad pa'i dus byung na /
NK036(chi)030:1005: chos khral la bcad thang mi byed pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:1006: dad rdzas phyag tu ci byung ba'i sum gnyis tshes
NK036(chi)030:1007: bcu dang tshes brgyad la btang zhing sum cha gcig
NK036(chi)030:1009: bu slob gzigs skyong mdzad pa'i dam bca' brtan po mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:1010: dad zas chud mi gson pa'i ched du /
NK036(chi)030:1012: tshes brgyad kyi zan yang sings po dang dar bas bardzi zhing /
NK036(chi)030:1013: spyan lam du 'byung ba'i bza' btung dngos po mchod pa gnyis la dmigs sgom byas pa la /
NK036(chi)030:1014: che btsun gal po cher byas pa su byung yang /
NK036(chi)030:1015: 'di zongs pas mi 'ju gsung nas mi gnang /
NK036(chi)030:1016: 'gyed mdzad dus gral mtho ba rnams kyi skal ba chad dogs med gsungs nas /
NK036(chi)030:1018: bkur sti dge 'dun la dgos pa yin /
NK036(chi)030:1019: sdig can rnams la mi dgos gsung nas skya nag la mi gnang /
NK036(chi)030:1020: chen por 'dod pa rnams la gdan mi 'ding /
NK036(chi)030:1021: bkur sti mi mdzad pa ni thugs kyi dam bca' yin /
NK036(chi)030:1022: 'byor ldan phyug po rnams kyi tshogs gsog dang 'bul ba ci tsam byas kyang /
NK036(chi)030:1023: chos dad gus kyi sgo nas bsgrubs pa yin phyag byed bzang /
NK036(chi)030:1024: thugs la btags zhal du mi 'don /
NK036(chi)030:1025: brdab lan dang gnang sbyin mi mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:1026: byas na tshong du 'gro bas khong rang gi dngos po de chud zos yin /
NK036(chi)030:1027: sh+aakya thub pa la ras yug gser srang stong ri ba phul yang /
NK036(chi)030:1028: bsngo ba mdzad pa ma gtogs pa gnang sbyin mdzad pa'i srol med /
NK036(chi)030:1029: tshogs bsags dang chos 'don la sogs pa yon bdag gis bya rgyu yin /
NK036(chi)030:1030: yon mchod go log na nan ltar mi bzang gsung /
NK036(chi)030:1031: 'dul ba lung la sogs gtam rgyud lung 'dren mang bar mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:1032: sprang po la sogs pa nyam chung gis skyo ra
NK036(chi)030:1033: nag po gcig drangs na yang zhim zhim ltar gsol
NK036(chi)030:1034: / mdo bsngo dang yon bshad rgyas pa re mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:1035: tshogs gnyis mkha' la sgrib gnyis chu 'dzin bral //
NK036(chi)030:1036: mkhyen pa'i nyi gzhon 'od stong lhag ge bas //
NK036(chi)030:1037: skal ldan rnams kyi 'dab stong rgyas pa dang //
NK036(chi)030:1038: mnyam du skye dgu'i rkang drug tshim mdzad bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1039: de nas tshogs pa la dbang khrid shin tu rgyas par mdzad nas /
NK036(chi)030:1040: rgyab chos gsung pa'i nyin gcig gi skabs na /
NK036(chi)030:1041: rgyal sras bzod pas spor phor dang bcas nang du gdan drangs pa'i tshe yang /
NK036(chi)030:1042: khyod la brel ba med na /
NK036(chi)030:1043: mkha' 'gro snying thig gi dras kha'i shog bu 'ga'
NK036(chi)030:1044: dros gsung tshar ba dang skas de phar bsgyur la
NK036(chi)030:1045: su yang ma btang bar smyug gu tshugs gsung nas
NK036(chi)030:1046: / zhal chems dri ma med pa'i 'od sprad pa'i skabs su /
NK036(chi)030:1047: da ni mi sdod pad+ma las 'brel rtsal //
NK036(chi)030:1048: 'chi med bde chen btsan sa 'dzin du 'gro //
NK036(chi)030:1049: tshe zad las zad smon lam 'phen pa zad //
NK036(chi)030:1050: gsung pa'i skabs su rgyal sras bzod pa spyan chab kyis brnang bzhin du /
NK036(chi)030:1051: phyag btsal nas gsol ba btab cing rten 'brel ngan
NK036(chi)030:1052: pa 'di 'dra ba mi gsung bar zhu zhus pas
NK036(chi)030:1054: da lta dal ba'i dus su byas pas da gzod brel ba'i dus na phan pa yin gsung nas /
NK036(chi)030:1055: bu slob spyi la zhal chems dri ma med pa'i
NK036(chi)030:1056: 'od dang sgos su snying thig pa rnams la zhal
NK036(chi)030:1057: chems gnad kyi me long gnyis mdzad nas /
NK036(chi)030:1058: mkha' 'gro snying thig gi po ti'i nang du bcugs /
NK036(chi)030:1059: 'di 'dra byas su la yang ma smra gsungs so //
NK036(chi)030:1060: gshegs par dgongs nas sras kyi thu bo la //
NK036(chi)030:1061: zhal chems bzhag nas mngon shes yod par bstan //
NK036(chi)030:1062: mthong spangs ma rig tshogs las dben pa yin //
NK036(chi)030:1063: 'jam dbyangs dngos su bstan la gus pas bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1064: de nas chos nyan 'brel ba yod pa rnams so sor gyes /
NK036(chi)030:1065: bla ma slob dpon rnams dang chos nyan grwa pa
NK036(chi)030:1066: nams kyis dbang gong ma la sogs pa'i zhu ba
NK036(chi)030:1067: byas pas / 'di gu ru jo 'ber gyis kyang ma gnang ba'i chos yin mi 'ong gsung /
NK036(chi)030:1069: 'o na khrid gnyer ngan pa de rnams kyis spyang ki byed par yod 'dug /
NK036(chi)030:1070: khrid gnyer ba barjesa gsung nas /
NK036(chi)030:1071: dbang zhu ba rnams la dmigs pa phog nas ri la btang ste /
NK036(chi)030:1072: rim pa bzhin du dbang mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:1074: theg mchog rin po che'i mdzod /
NK036(chi)030:1075: yang tig yid bzhin nor bu dang bcas pa rdzogs par gsung /
NK036(chi)030:1076: chos thon pa'i tshogs 'khor gyi nang par rang re
NK036(chi)030:1077: dpon slob zab mo'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor nas
NK036(chi)030:1078: / tshogs kyi dga' ston byed pa yang da nang tsam du gda' 'o //
NK036(chi)030:1079: khyed rang gzhan don nus pa rnams kyis skal ba
NK036(chi)030:1080: dang ldan pa'i slob ma gang byung la rang 'dod
NK036(chi)030:1084: damachosa nyams su len pa rnams 'jig rten gyi bya ba don du ma gnyer bar /
NK036(chi)030:1085: khregs chod dang thod rgal gyi don la mnyam par zhog /
NK036(chi)030:1086: ma go ba'i skabs byung na kho bos byas pa'i
NK036(chi)030:1087: yang thig yid bzhin nor bu 'di nor bu bsam
NK036(chi)030:1088: 'phel dang 'dra ba yin pas blta rtogs zhib mo
NK036(chi)030:1090: 'khor ba zad sar bskyal nas myang 'das kyi sa la slebs par 'gyur ro //
NK036(chi)030:1092: gnam g.yogs bral ba'i mkhas la mtha' dbus med //
NK036(chi)030:1093: lta sgom rdzogs la srid zhi mnyam pa nyid //
NK036(chi)030:1094: zad sar bskyal bas kun bzang dgongs pa rdzogs //
NK036(chi)030:1095: chos rje klong chen rab 'byams dad brgyas mchod //
NK036(chi)030:1096: de nas zhwa'i lha khang gi gtsug lag khang gi nyams gso rnams mdzad pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:1097: mchod pa 'bul ba la 'byon pa'i skabs su /
NK036(chi)030:1098: chos skyong la gsol ka mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:1099: khrom la chos gsung pa'i tshe me tog gi char rtsod pa med par babs /
NK036(chi)030:1100: thams cad la thar pa'i sa bon thebs par mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:1101: chu bo rir phyag phebs pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:1104: yon bdag rnams la yang mi 'thad pa 'ga' re 'byung bar 'dug /
NK036(chi)030:1105: kho bos khyed rnams la mya ngan mi 'jog gsung /
NK036(chi)030:1106: de nas bsam yas pa'i dud gtong drug gi gdan 'dren byung bas /
NK036(chi)030:1107: rgya mar zhag shas gcig bzhugs nas la la byon
NK036(chi)030:1108: pa'i tho rangs 'jam dbyangs kun dga' rgyal mtshan pa
NK036(chi)030:1109: la sogs pa bla ma slob dpon /
NK036(chi)030:1110: yon bdag bu slob dang bcas pas skyel thung byas nas /
NK036(chi)030:1111: rgya ma yun thang du phyags phebs pas chibs las gzhol nas /
NK036(chi)030:1112: sa 'ja' li'i steng na bzhugs te /
NK036(chi)030:1113: da khyed rang rnams phyir log 'phreng ba las mi yong /
NK036(chi)030:1114: khyed rnams kyis kyang da nang nas nga mthong ba min /
NK036(chi)030:1116: nged dum pa zhig 'dir 'dug gsungs pas /
NK036(chi)030:1117: thams cad kyi gdong mchi mas khebs te so sor gyes /
NK036(chi)030:1118: de nas la la byon nas mchims phur phyags phebs pa'i nyin par /
NK036(chi)030:1119: 'o rgya gar gyi dur khrod bsil ba tshal gyi dod po yin pas /
NK036(chi)030:1120: gzhan du skyes pa bas 'dir shi bar dga' bar bshad /
NK036(chi)030:1121: nga'i sgyu lus kyi phung po 'di yang mchims phur dur khrod chen po 'dir 'jog /
NK036(chi)030:1122: bsam pa cig kyang thog tu phebs pa yin gsung /
NK036(chi)030:1123: dud gtong drug gis thog drangs pa'i phyogs nas 'dus pa'i tshogs pa rnams la khrid btab /
NK036(chi)030:1124: tshogs pa ches pas spros med kyi dbang la zhag grangs mang rabs shig song ba'i skabs su /
NK036(chi)030:1125: bsnyungs pa'i tshul bstan yang nub re bzhin dbang mdzad /
NK036(chi)030:1126: bcu drug gi nyen par mchod gtor shom dbang byed gsung pas /
NK036(chi)030:1127: sku bsnyungs pas 'o brgyal zhags gsu ma sku ngal gso bar mdzad pa zhus pas /
NK036(chi)030:1128: de mi dgos dbang 'di tshar ba zhig byed gsung
NK036(chi)030:1129: pa la nan gyis zhus pas dbang 'di tshar ba
NK036(chi)030:1130: zhig byed bsam pa yin te /
NK036(chi)030:1131: khyed rnams mi nyan par 'dug gsung nas steng du bzhud /
NK036(chi)030:1132: de nas chu mo yos kyi lo lnga bcu rtsa
NK036(chi)030:1133: drug bzhes pa la rgyal gyi zla ba'i tshes bco
NK036(chi)030:1134: brgyad kyi dro khar song ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:1136: slob dpon kun dpal la sogs pa 'ga' zhig drung
NK036(chi)030:1137: du yod pa la mchod pa gcig shom la khyed
NK036(chi)030:1139: nged rnams mi 'gro 'dir 'dug par zhu zhus pas /
NK036(chi)030:1140: 'o na sgyu lus gog po 'di 'dor ba yin pas /
NK036(chi)030:1141: khyed rang rnams zhad mi dgos /
NK036(chi)030:1142: ca co ma byed par mnyam gzhag la sdod gsungs
NK036(chi)030:1143: nas chos sku'i bzhugs stangs kyis gdod ma'i sar gshegs
NK036(chi)030:1144: so // kye ma kyi hud skyabs gnas thugs rje can //
NK036(chi)030:1145: rgya mtsho'i gon can 'di dag dang mtshungs su //
NK036(chi)030:1146: da ni mi bzhugs gdod ma'i sar gshegs pa //
NK036(chi)030:1147: bdag cag skal ba ldan rnams 'dor phod dam //
NK036(chi)030:1148: bshes bral dmus long thang chen dbus lhung ltar //
NK036(chi)030:1149: mgon po khyed min bdag cag su la re //
NK036(chi)030:1150: byang chub ljon shing rkang 'thung chag gyur pas //
NK036(chi)030:1151: sdug bsngal tshad pas gdungs la bsil byed su //
NK036(chi)030:1152: dpal ldan yon tan dpag med 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK036(chi)030:1153: mya ngan 'das pa'i 'brog dgon der gshegs pas //
NK036(chi)030:1154: lhar bcas rnams kyi gtsug rgyan rin po che //
NK036(chi)030:1155: yengs ma skabs la stor zhing mgon med gyur //
NK036(chi)030:1156: smra ba'i seng ge skyes mchog chen pos kyang //
NK036(chi)030:1157: bas mtha'i nags su ded dpon stong pa ltar //
NK036(chi)030:1158: de ring bdag snying mya ngan chen pos gdungs //
NK036(chi)030:1159: da ni dbyings nas thugs rjes gzigs 'tshal lo //
NK036(chi)030:1160: zhes pa ni smre sngags kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK036(chi)030:1161: de nas rgyal gyi zla ba dang /
NK036(chi)030:1162: cho 'phrul gyi ring la nyin mtshan med par 'aja'i gur phub /
NK036(chi)030:1163: me tog gi sil ma bkram /
NK036(chi)030:1166: der tshogs pa'i skal ldan 'ga' zhig la /
NK036(chi)030:1167: 'od gsal gyi snang bas phyam brdal bar gyur /
NK036(chi)030:1168: zhag nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bar sku gdung bzhugs pa la /
NK036(chi)030:1170: ga bur gyi dri zil gyis non pa'i dri ngad bzang pos khyab par gyur /
NK036(chi)030:1171: zhal ta la gdung khang gsar pa ma brtsig par /
NK036(chi)030:1172: rnying pa zhig tu khyer la bzhus gsungs pas /
NK036(chi)030:1173: mchod pa'i sprin phung mang po dang bcas gdung khang rnying pa zhig tu gdan drangs pa'i tshe /
NK036(chi)030:1174: sa chen po 'di rab tu g.yos shing /
NK036(chi)030:1175: 'ur 'ur chem chem pa'i sgra lan bdun du grags par gyur to //
NK036(chi)030:1176: thub pa'i dbang po ku shi'i tshal gzims tshe //
NK036(chi)030:1177: nyan thos rnams kyang mya ngan gyis gdungs ltar //
NK036(chi)030:1178: dri med 'od zer mchims phur gzims pa'i tshe //
NK036(chi)030:1179: mthong thos rnams kyang mya ngan zug rngus gzir //
NK036(chi)030:1180: mkha' klong yangs pa'i dbyings kyang ma rdibs la //
NK036(chi)030:1181: 'byung ba 'dzin ma 'di yang ma chags na //
NK036(chi)030:1182: chu gter chen po 'khrugs par ma gyur cing //
NK036(chi)030:1183: bdag cag rnams la 'di ltar gyur 'di ci //
NK036(chi)030:1185: thugs ljags spyan gsum gdung khang nas 'phar te /
NK036(chi)030:1186: skal ba dang ldan pa'i pang du byon pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:1187: rigs lnga'i rang bzhin thob pa'i rtags su /
NK036(chi)030:1188: sha r+ai ram la sogs pa gdung rigs lnga dang /
NK036(chi)030:1189: ring bsrel phra mo grangs las 'das shing 'phel gdung du gyur nas /
NK036(chi)030:1190: re re la yang brgya phrag 'phel zhing da lta'i
NK036(chi)030:1191: bar du 'phel ba kun gyis mthong zhing rtsod pa
NK036(chi)030:1192: med do // 'di ni chos kyi sku las gzugs kyi skur bzhengs te /
NK036(chi)030:1193: gdul bya'i khams dang mos pa ji lta ba bzhin
NK036(chi)030:1194: du 'chad rtsod rtsom gsum la spobs pa thogs pa
NK036(chi)030:1196: de la sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi bstan pa
NK036(chi)030:1197: dam pa'i chos rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa bsam
NK036(chi)030:1198: gyis mi khyab pa dag las /
NK036(chi)030:1199: dam pa rnams kyi bka' drin la brten nas kho
NK036(chi)030:1200: bo cag gi khong du chud pa'i don phyi rabs
NK036(chi)030:1201: kyi gdul bya rnams kyis rtogs par sla ba'i phyir
NK036(chi)030:1202: bstan bcos su bkod pa la /
NK036(chi)030:1205: de kho na nyid kyi gnas gsum du rnam par bzhag pas /
NK036(chi)030:1206: dang po ni gsung rab la 'jug pa'i them skas
NK036(chi)030:1207: sam thun mong du gyur pa dag gi phyogs su
NK036(chi)030:1209: yi ge'i sdeb sbyor la 'jug pa rin chen snye ma 1che chung 2gnyis /
NK036(chi)030:1210: rig pa klog pa'i don bsdus3 /
NK036(chi)030:1212: klog gi bstan bcos zla ba gsal byed5 /
NK036(chi)030:1213: sdeb sbyor la 'jug pa nyi ma'i shing rta6 /
NK036(chi)030:1214: lci yang gi gnas pa rin po che'i lde mig7 /
NK036(chi)030:1215: mngon brjod la 'jug pa me tog gi 'khri shing 8 /
NK036(chi)030:1216: snyan ngag gi bstan bcos me tog rgyas pa'i skyed mos tshal9 /
NK036(chi)030:1217: dper brjod kyi gnas nges pa klu shing gi me tog10 /
NK036(chi)030:1218: spel ma'i gnas la 'jug pa tshangs pa'i gsung dbyangs

NK036(chi)030:1498: rdzogs pa chen po chos nyid rang grol240 /

NK036(chi)030:1501: rdzogs pa chen po mnyam nyid rang grol243 /
NK036(chi)030:1503: khrid yig chos sku lhun grub rnams dang 245 /
NK036(chi)030:1504: klong sde spyi'i don bshad la /
NK036(chi)030:1505: klong gsum spyi'i don bshad chings246 /

NK036(chi)030:1509: khrid yig khyab brdal klong yangs rnams dang 250 /
NK036(chi)030:1510: man ngag sde'i spyi don bshad pa la /

NK036(chi)030:1513: mtshan dpe sku gsum lag khrid253 /
NK036(chi)030:1514: man ngag gi don 'grel kun 'dus rig pa'i gal mdo254 /
NK036(chi)030:1516: bar do 'od kyi snye man 256 la sogs zab cing rgya che ba'i gnas bstan pa lags so //
NK036(chi)030:1517: yang zab chos mchog nges don snying po'i mkhar //
NK036(chi)030:1518: sku dang ye shes nyi ma'i 'od brdal bas //
NK036(chi)030:1519: bla med bstan pa 'i pad tshal rgyas pa dang //
NK036(chi)030:1520: mnyam du gdul bya'i bya tshogs dga' bar shog /
NK036(chi)030:1521: don gnyis pa gsang chen bla na med pa'i gnas mdo spyi dang bye brag tu bshad pa la /
NK036(chi)030:1522: spyi'i chings rgya cher bstan pa dang /
NK036(chi)030:1523: bye brag zab don snying por bsdu ba gnyis las /
NK036(chi)030:1524: re zhig gsang chen nges pa theg pa'i rgyal po'i
NK036(chi)030:1525: rnam bzhag yo ga'i phyogs kyi don du phab pa'i
NK036(chi)030:1526: gnas gsal byed grub mtha' rin po che'i mdzod257 /
NK036(chi)030:1527: rgyud bcu bdun man ngag brgya dang bcu dgu'i don 'grel theg mchog rin po che'i mdzod258 /
NK036(chi)030:1528: lam khyer gnad kyi don 'grel tshig don rin po che'i mdzod259 /
NK036(chi)030:1529: chings nges pa man ngag rin po che gser gyi sgrom bu260 /
NK036(chi)030:1530: bye brag zab don snying por bsdu ba la /
NK036(chi)030:1531: khrid kyi yi ge sems sbyong bdun pa161 /
NK036(chi)030:1534: man ngag gi lung rdzogs par ston pa bla ma
NK036(chi)030:1535: yang thig yid bzhin nor bu chos sdee lnga bcu
NK036(chi)030:1536: rtsa bzhi pa264 / de las shin tu zab pa'i
NK036(chi)030:1537: gnas bsdu ba zab mo yang tig chos tshan sum
NK036(chi)030:1538: cu 265 rtsa lnga pa rnams ni bla ma snying
NK036(chi)030:1539: tig byin rlabs lag khrid kyi skor dang /
NK036(chi)030:1540: khyad par du smon lam lung bstan dang 'brel ba
NK036(chi)030:1541: mkha' 'gro snying thig gi skor la man ngag dus
NK036(chi)030:1542: la babs pa / mkha' 'gro lung bstan gyi bab lugs ngo bo lag khrid du bstan pa266 /
NK036(chi)030:1543: dbang khrid gdams pa'i mtshon tshul267 /
NK036(chi)030:1544: byin brlabs sems la shar ba nges don snying po'i
NK036(chi)030:1545: gdams pa ste gnad gsum chos sde lnga bcu rtsa
NK036(chi)030:1546: lngar gtan la phab pa ni mkha' 'gro yang tig
NK036(chi)030:1547: gi chos kyi rnam grangs so268 //
NK036(chi)030:1548: zhar la chos spyod las rim gsol 'debs drug pa269 /
NK036(chi)030:1550: rdo rje'i glu sum cu dang bcas pa rnams ni de dag gi cha lag tu bstan pa ste /
NK036(chi)030:1551: shin tu zab pa'i yang zab ngo mtshar rmad du
NK036(chi)030:1552: byung ba'i skor du gtogs pa rnams phyi rabs skal
NK036(chi)030:1553: ldan rnams kyi don du bum thang thar pa gling
NK036(chi)030:1554: du dkar chag la btab pa gu ru'i lugs su
NK036(chi)030:1555: chos rje rin po che'i sku gsung thugs che ba'i
NK036(chi)030:1556: yon tan bstan pa'i phyir rnam par thar pa gsal
NK036(chi)030:1558: ngag gi dbang pos 'chad lugs mthong tsa na //
NK036(chi)030:1559: sku mched gsum po'i chos 'chad dig dig po //
NK036(chi)030:1560: klong chen rab 'byams rig grwar rtsod tsa na //
NK036(chi)030:1561: phya gtsang dan gsum rtsod pa rkyang rkyang po //
NK036(chi)030:1562: kun mkhyen chen po'i rtsom pa mthong tsa na //
NK036(chi)030:1563: bu dol sher gsum rtsom pa mog mog po //
NK036(chi)030:1564: sna tshogs rang grol lta dgongs mthong tsa na //
NK036(chi)030:1565: chen po gsum gyi grub mtha' yu yu po //
NK036(chi)030:1566: phan pa bzang po'i mdzad spyod mthong tsa na //
NK036(chi)030:1567: chen por 'dod pa'i spyod pa dman dman 'dra //
NK036(chi)030:1568: pad+ma las 'brel yon tan mthong tsa na //
NK036(chi)030:1569: rtogs ldan ming btags rnams kyang blun blun po //
NK036(chi)030:1570: gu yangs blo bde'i bya bral mthong tsa na //
NK036(chi)030:1571: bzang po zhig po'i spyod pa dman dman 'dra //
NK036(chi)030:1572: dri med 'od zer gzhan don mthong tsa na //
NK036(chi)030:1573: chen por rlom rnams gzhan don lad mo 'dra //
NK036(chi)030:1574: zhes pa 'di yang bdag nyid chen po 'di gzhan las ches mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK036(chi)030:1575: tshogs gnyis rba rlabs ye shes chu gter can //
NK036(chi)030:1576: mkhyen rtse'i lbu phreng ri dbang brtsegs ngog rol //
NK036(chi)030:1577: dbang bzhi'i chu rgyun skye dgu'i dri ma sbyong //
NK036(chi)030:1578: bden gnyis dal 'babs de la gus pas bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1579: thugs rje klu dbang mkhyen brtse'i gdengs kas mdzes //
NK036(chi)030:1580: nus stobs gru char skye rgu'i zhing sar gshin //
NK036(chi)030:1581: byams pa'i phung sgra phyogs kyi mthar khyab pa //
NK036(chi)030:1582: skyabs chen chu lha de la gus pas bstod //

NK036(chi)030:1590: rjes 'jug rkang drug bcud kyis rgyas mdzad bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1591: sbyin pa rnam bzhis gzhan rgyud tshim mdzad nas //
