NK036(chi)030:1593: bzod pa gsum gyis dkar thub mthar phyin nas //
NK036(chi)030:1594: rgyud gsum thugs dgongs rdzogs mdzad de la bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1595: brtson 'grus gsum gyis don gnyis legs grub nas //
NK036(chi)030:1596: bsam gtan gsum gyis rigs dang mngon shes grub //
NK036(chi)030:1597: shes rab gsum gyis a ti'i rtse mor son //
NK036(chi)030:1598: kun bzang chos kyi rje der dad brgyas bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1599: rim gnyis thabs kyis ye shes stobs dang ldan //
NK036(chi)030:1600: dus gsum dge ba 'khor gsum dag par bsngo //
NK036(chi)030:1601: gnas lugs ji ltar shes bya ji snyed mkhyen //
NK036(chi)030:1602: 'jam dbyangs dngos su byon der gus pas bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1603: byams pa'i spyan gyis 'gro la rtag tu gzigs //
NK036(chi)030:1604: snying rjes sdug phongs rnams la rtag tu skyong //
NK036(chi)030:1605: dga' dang dgyes pas 'gro rnams srid mtshor sgrol //
NK036(chi)030:1606: dgra dang bu mnyam 'gro don g.yel ba med //
NK036(chi)030:1607: tshad med bzhin ldan de la gus pas bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1608: chos dang zang zing g.yab mos gdul bya 'bod //
NK036(chi)030:1609: snyan smra'i gsung gis nges pa'i chos la sbyor //
NK036(chi)030:1610: don mthun chos la bgas phab a tir sbyor //
NK036(chi)030:1611: bsdu ba bzhi yis 'gro don mdzad la bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1612: thos pas sde snod rgyud sde'i don la mkhas //
NK036(chi)030:1613: bsam pas zab don snying tig yin par rtogs //
NK036(chi)030:1614: bsgoms pas kun tu bzang po'i sa la slebs //
NK036(chi)030:1615: sangs rgyas bshes gnyen gzugs su sprul la bstod //
NK036(chi)030:1616: ces pa 'di ni sgo gsum gus pa'i sgo nas /
NK036(chi)030:1617: chos rje rin po che'i mkhyen rab phrin las kyi
NK036(chi)030:1618: mdzad pa la thun mong ma yin pa'i sgo nas
NK036(chi)030:1619: dad pa'i rlabs g.yo bas mngon par bstod cing gtsug
NK036(chi)030:1620: tu khur ba'o // grwa phu bsam yas gsang phu skyam gyi phu //
NK036(chi)030:1621: lha ring brag dang shug gseb o rgyan rdzong //
NK036(chi)030:1622: rgya ma grong dang g.yor po gzhung rnams dang //
NK036(chi)030:1623: lho brag mon yul rnams su zhabs kyis bcags //
NK036(chi)030:1624: skal ldan rnams la thar pa'i sa bon btab //
NK036(chi)030:1625: chos 'khor bskor zhing smin grol rgya cher mdzad //
NK036(chi)030:1626: tha ma'i mdzad pa mchims phur myang 'das mdzad //
NK036(chi)030:1627: skyes mchog bzhugs pa'i gnas rnams la phyag 'tshal //
NK036(chi)030:1628: de ltar legs par sbyar ba'i chos rje rin po che'i rnam par thar pa 'di ni /
NK036(chi)030:1629: lung rig 'dzin pa sprul sku dpal 'byor rgya mtsho dang /
NK036(chi)030:1630: dad dang gus par ldan pas mnyes pa gsum bsgrubs pa /
NK036(chi)030:1631: dam tshig dang ldan pa'i slob dpon blo gros bzang
NK036(chi)030:1632: po dpon slob gnyis kyis yang dang yang du nan
NK036(chi)030:1633: gyis bskul bas rang gis rtogs tshogs dang /
NK036(chi)030:1634: rgyal sras rin po che bzod pa sku lus grib ma bzhin du brten pas /
NK036(chi)030:1635: gsung sgros dang mdzad tshul rnams legs par zhus nas /
NK036(chi)030:1636: 'phri ba snan dang lhag chad med par yi ger btab pa'o //
NK036(chi)030:1637: rta bdun rgyal po'i 'od kyis ma gsal zhing //
NK036(chi)030:1638: chu gter chen po'i rlabs kyis ma gsher ba //
NK036(chi)030:1639: sangs rgyas rabs bdun gyis kyang ma thul ba'i //
NK036(chi)030:1640: gdul dka' 'dul mdzad skyes mchog rnam thar 'di //
NK036(chi)030:1641: sgro skur spangs nas legs par bkod pa yin //
NK036(chi)030:1642: zas gtsang sras po mtshan dpes brgyan pa yi //
NK036(chi)030:1643: zhabs pad nyi gzhon lta bur dmar ba la //
NK036(chi)030:1644: gtsug tu khur ba'i lha chen gdong bzhi dang //
NK036(chi)030:1645: me tog pad+mo'i gnyen la sogs pa'ang //
NK036(chi)030:1646: mthong ba don ldan 'di nyid rtogs gyur na //
NK036(chi)030:1647: dgyes pa'i spyan 'byed bzang pos mdangs phyung nas //
NK036(chi)030:1648: mngon par bstod cing dga' ston 'gyed par nges //
NK036(chi)030:1650: gsang ba'i snying thig dbang gi rgyal po bzhin //
NK036(chi)030:1651: dgos 'dod kun 'byung srid zhi'i dbul ba sel //
NK036(chi)030:1652: 'di don rtogs par 'dod pa mang na yang //
NK036(chi)030:1653: ston ka'i mtshan mo dwangs pa'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK036(chi)030:1654: ri bong 'dzin gzugs 'od dkar can shar bas //
NK036(chi)030:1655: dman pa'i skar tshogs kha dog nyams byas ltar //
NK036(chi)030:1656: kho bo 'chad rtsod rtsom gsum rab rgyas pas //
NK036(chi)030:1657: rdo rje pha lam rin chen 'bigs pa ltar //
NK036(chi)030:1658: tshig don rnams bkra bsam 'phel phreng spel nas //
NK036(chi)030:1659: legs bshad srad bur brgyud pa'i phreng ba 'di //
NK036(chi)030:1660: rnam thar nor bu chu dwangs ji bzhin du //
NK036(chi)030:1661: sems kyi rnyog pa ma lus sel byed yin //
NK036(chi)030:1662: dri med 'od zer blta ba'i me long mchog /
NK036(chi)030:1663: tshul khrims blo gros yos tan rgyas par bstan //
NK036(chi)030:1664: snga rabs byon dang ma 'ongs slad kyis 'byon /
NK036(chi)030:1665: sus kyang ma rtogs rtogs par mi 'gyur ro //
NK036(chi)030:1666: kho bos blo gros nam mkha' yangs pa la //
NK036(chi)030:1667: thos bsam chu 'dzin rab tu rgyas pa yis //
NK036(chi)030:1668: lung dang rig pa'i glog phreng gar byed pas //
NK036(chi)030:1669: rtogs pa'i 'brug sgra chem chem sgrogs pa dang //
NK036(chi)030:1670: mnyam du dam chos chu rgyun 'bebs pa yin //
NK036(chi)030:1671: dge bcu'i lo thog smin par byed pa la //
NK036(chi)030:1672: skye ba sngon nas sbyangs pa'i shes rab can //
NK036(chi)030:1673: rigs dang spyod yul bzang po'i rnam grol can //
NK036(chi)030:1674: slob ma'i mchog gyur ka bzhi 'dzin pa po //
NK036(chi)030:1675: rang bzhin dpal 'byor bzang po 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK036(chi)030:1676: dam chos rgya mtshos 'gro ba smin mdzad pa'i //
NK036(chi)030:1677: rdzogs chen bstan pa 'dzin pa'i skyes bu dang //
NK036(chi)030:1678: blo gros rnam par dkar ba'i ngur smrig 'dzin //
NK036(chi)030:1679: bzang po'i spyod yul sdom gsum dam tshig ldan //
NK036(chi)030:1680: thos bsam don gzhol bla ma ci mnyes byed //
NK036(chi)030:1681: rdo rje snying po'i brtul zhugs 'dzin pa dang //
NK036(chi)030:1682: dpon slob gnyis kyis yang yang bskul ba'i ngor //
NK036(chi)030:1683: rnam thar mthong ba don ldan 'di spros pas //
NK036(chi)030:1684: 'gro ba'i rmongs pa ma lus rab bsal nas //
NK036(chi)030:1685: rdzogs pa chen po'i don la spyod pa dang //
NK036(chi)030:1686: don gnyis phun tshogs 'grub pa'i rgyal por shog /
NK036(chi)030:1687: yi ge pa ni skye ba sngon rol nas //
NK036(chi)030:1688: chos la sbyangs pa'i bsod nams dpal ldan can //
NK036(chi)030:1689: blo gsal theg mchog snying po'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK036(chi)030:1690: a ti yo ga 'chang bas legs par bris //
NK036(chi)030:1691: dge ba dpag yas rin chen gru bo ches //
NK036(chi)030:1692: 'gro drug ma rnams srid pa'i mtsho bsgral nas //
NK036(chi)030:1693: mi g.yo rin chen gling du rab son te //
NK036(chi)030:1694: dam pa'i chos kyi dga' ston 'gyed par shog /
NK036(chi)030:1695: bkra shis gang zhig sku bzhi'i gangs ri las //
NK036(chi)030:1696: dam chos yan lag brgyad ldan chu klung gis //
NK036(chi)030:1697: 'gro ba'i tsha gdung ma lus zhi ba dang //
NK036(chi)030:1698: mnyam du dge legs phun sum tshogs gyur cig /
NK036(chi)030:1699: rgyal sras dri med 'od zer gyi //
NK036(chi)030:1700: rnam thar mthong ba don ldan 'di //
NK036(chi)030:1701: byang phyogs gangs kyi ri khrod du //
NK036(chi)030:1702: byar med brtul zhugs 'dzin pa yi //
NK036(chi)030:1703: chogs grags bzang po mdo khams pa //
NK036(chi)030:1704: pha yi bu mchog de yis bkod //
NK036(chi)030:1705: legs par ltos la zhib mor dpyod //
NK036(chi)030:1706: 'di ni tshangs pa'i rnga chen dang //
NK036(chi)030:1707: rab dag'i rgyud mngas las 'phags shing //
NK036(chi)030:1709: 'di sogs dge ba rab dkar dri med des //
NK036(chi)030:1710: spangs rtogs yon tan du mas mdzod 'dzin pa'i //
NK036(chi)030:1711: ded dpon bla ma rnams ni mnyes byas nas //
NK036(chi)030:1712: kun bzang gdod ma'i sa la rab gnas shog ///
